A105%2C%22height%22%3A29%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%5B5%2C%5D%22%2C%22x%22%3A687%2C%22y%22%3A447%2C%22width%22%3A65%2C%22height%22%3A35%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%5B1%2C3%5D%22%2C%22x%22%3A504%2C%22y%22%3A56%2C%22width%22%3A89%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%5B5%2C%22%2C%22x%22%3A501%2C%22y%22%3A270%2C%22width%22%3A44%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f9f9f9%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ub028612a%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;ud8173154\&quot;" data-lake-indent="\&quot;2\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u86e521d1\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ucd131572\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucd131572\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2ada805c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2ada805c\&quot;">当客户端 1 收到大多数的接受者（节点 A、B）的准备响应后，根据响应中提案编号最大的提案的值，设置接受请求中的值。因为该值在来自节点 A、B 的准备响应中都为空（也就是图 5 中的“尚无提案”），所以就把自己的提议值 3 作为提案的值，发送接受请求 [1, 3]。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;u86e521d1\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u246f0e88\&quot;" id="\&quot;u246f0e88\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9043b195\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9043b195\&quot;">当客户端 2 收到大多数的接受者的准备响应后（节点 A、B 和节点 C），根据响应中提案编号最大的提案的值，来设置接受请求中的值。因为该值在来自节点 A、B、C 的准备响应中都为空（也就是图 5 和图 6 中的“尚无提案”），所以就把自己的提议值 7 作为提案的值，发送接受请求 [5, 7]。</span></li>
  </ul>
  <ol list="\&quot;ub391059a\&quot;" start="\&quot;2\&quot;" data-lake-indent="\&quot;1\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u2330b0a9\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ufee347b3\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufee347b3\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5f56edae\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5f56edae\&quot;">当三个节点收到 2 个客户端的接受请求时，会进行这样的处理：</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u85b3b7c5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u85b3b7c5\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-indent:" 2em;="" padding-left:="" 2em\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733482295970-11e458b2-f87b-4b82-9456-0407185d3b22.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ub67961ba-c1f2-4377-8497-2718d0747a0%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u860f4ff9-3604-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A635%2C%22height%22%3A243%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A372301%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1354%2C%22originHeight%22%3A518%2C%22ratio%22%3A1%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%8F%90%E8%AE%AE%E8%80%85(%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E7%AB%AF2%22%2C%22x%22%3A21%2C%22y%22%3A153%2C%22width%22%3A245%2C%22height%22%3A36%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E8%80%85(%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A)%22%2C%22x%22%3A21%2C%22y%22%3A238%2C%22width%22%3A224%2C%22height%22%3A37%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E8%80%85(%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E5%BF%83)%22%2C%22x%22%3A20%2C%22y%22%3A407%2C%22width%22%3A225%2C%22height%22%3A39%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E8%80%85(%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B)%22%2C%22x%22%3A23%2C%22y%22%3A324%2C%22width%22%3A217%2C%22height%22%3A36%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%8F%90%E8%AE%AE%E8%80%85(%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E7%AB%AF1)%22%2C%22x%22%3A22%2C%22y%22%3A65%2C%22width%22%3A251%2C%22height%22%3A36%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%22%2C%22x%22%3A460%2C%22y%22%3A13%2C%22width%22%3A101%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%22%2C%22x%22%3A752%2C%22y%22%3A93%2C%22width%22%3A105%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%5B1%2C3%5D%22%2C%22x%22%3A465%2C%22y%22%3A50%2C%22width%22%3A84%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%5B5%2C7%5D%22%2C%22x%22%3A724%2C%22y%22%3A266%2C%22width%22%3A91%2C%22height%22%3A33%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%5B5%2C7%5D%22%2C%22x%22%3A928%2C%22y%22%3A444%2C%22width%22%3A86%2C%22height%22%3A32%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%5B5%2C7%5D%22%2C%22x%22%3A805%2C%22y%22%3A343%2C%22width%22%3A82%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%22%2C%22x%22%3A1208%2C%22y%22%3A457%2C%22width%22%3A74%2C%22height%22%3A37%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%5B5%2C7%5D%22%2C%22x%22%3A756%2C%22y%22%3A131%2C%22width%22%3A97%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f9f8f8%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u0583ad95%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;u8b0a9c87\&quot;" data-lake-indent="\&quot;2\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;ua7cf52ec\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u88b76b45\&quot;" id="\&quot;u88b76b45\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uef5cc726\&quot;" id="\&quot;uef5cc726\&quot;">当节点 A、B、C 收到接受请求 [1, 3] 的时候，由于提案的提案编号 1 小于三个节点承诺能通过的提案的最小提案编号 5，所以提案 [1, 3] 将被拒绝。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;ua7cf52ec\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u43dd515a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u43dd515a\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u78a5dac6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u78a5dac6\&quot;">当节点 A、B、C 收到接受请求 [5, 7] 的时候，由于提案的提案编号 5 不小于三个节点承诺能通过的提案的最小提案编号 5，所以就通过提案 [5, 7]，也就是接受了值 7，三个节点就 X 值为 7 达成了共识。</span></li>
  </ul>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua78a2ec8\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua78a2ec8\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u512e6133\&quot;" id="\&quot;u512e6133\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u3ffa00d6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3ffa00d6\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u534a1bc6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u534a1bc6\&quot;">​</span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u30d7303f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u30d7303f\&quot;">本质上而言，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ubfc244a5\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubfc244a5\&quot;">提案编号的大小代表着优先级</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6c214824\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6c214824\&quot;">，根据提案编号的大小，接受者保证</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucde072cc\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucde072cc\&quot;">三个承诺</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9ef5c193\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9ef5c193\&quot;">，具体来说：</span></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;ua98d0bf1\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u67a53cfd\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u514e47f3\&quot;" id="\&quot;u514e47f3\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc9b55a75\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc9b55a75\&quot;">如果准备请求的提案编号，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u339fcefb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u339fcefb\&quot;">小于等于</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uab7f974d\&quot;" id="\&quot;uab7f974d\&quot;">接受者已经响应的准备请求的提案编号，那么接受者将承诺不响应这个准备请求</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;u67a53cfd\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u0e5373f2\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0e5373f2\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6cfd75fd\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6cfd75fd\&quot;">如果接受请求中的提案的提案编号，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufa0c54b7\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufa0c54b7\&quot;">小于</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u46d4c652\&quot;" id="\&quot;u46d4c652\&quot;">接受者已经响应的准备请求的提案编号，那么接受者将承诺不通过这个提案</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;u67a53cfd\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ube8921c0\&quot;" id="\&quot;ube8921c0\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;udc77079c\&quot;" id="\&quot;udc77079c\&quot;">如果接受者之前有通过提案，那么接受者将承诺，会在准备请求的响应中，包含</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0de09d26\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0de09d26\&quot;">已经通过的最大编号的提案信息</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf6ce4f48\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf6ce4f48\&quot;">。</span></li>
  </ul>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ue07c2a35\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue07c2a35\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2fbfa410\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2fbfa410\&quot;">综上可知，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ueb263b03\&quot;" id="\&quot;ueb263b03\&quot;">大多数节点就某个值，达成共识后，值就不再变了，哪怕有新的提案，这个值也能保证不再变了。</span></strong></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u83d4d8a2\&quot;" id="\&quot;u83d4d8a2\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud6e8780c\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud6e8780c\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
  <blockquote data-lake-id="\&quot;uc4ee55ef\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc4ee55ef\&quot;">
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u0d4bfb59\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0d4bfb59\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ubf9e7736\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubf9e7736\&quot;">参考文章：</span></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ucdfd5df8\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucdfd5df8\&quot;">
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;bookmarkInline\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22mode%22%3A%22title%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2F100046101%2F201700%2F%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2F100046101%2F201700%2F%22%2C%22detail%22%3A%7B%22icon%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2Ffavicon.ico%22%2C%22image%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic001.geekbang.org%2Fresource%2Fimage%2Fdb%2F95%2Fdbab946f81227e16af56a4084ec51595.jpg%22%2C%22title%22%3A%2205%20%7C%20Paxos%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E9%97%B4%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E6%9F%90%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%80%BC%EF%BC%9F%22%2C%22belong%22%3A%22%E6%9E%81%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%B7%B2%E5%AE%8C%E7%BB%93%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E9%99%90%E6%97%B6%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB%22%2C%22belong_url%22%3Anull%2C%22desc%22%3A%22%E5%9C%A8%E8%BF%87%E5%8E%BB%E5%87%A0%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4%E9%87%8C%EF%BC%8CPaxos%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8A%E6%98%AF%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E5%85%B1%E8%AF%86%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%A3%E5%90%8D%E8%AF%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%BA%E5%BD%93%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%80%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E6%89%B9%E5%85%B1%E8%AF%86%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E5%AE%83%E6%94%B9%E8%BF%9B%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2F100046101%2F201700%2F%22%2C%22extra%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22_serializer%22%3A%22web.editor_link_detail%22%7D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Ku4np%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u251e2e79\&quot;" id="\&quot;u251e2e79\&quot;">
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;bookmarkInline\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22mode%22%3A%22title%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnblogs.com%2Flinbingdong%2Fp%2F6253479.html%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnblogs.com%2Flinbingdong%2Fp%2F6253479.html%22%2C%22detail%22%3A%7B%22icon%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fassets.cnblogs.com%2Ffavicon_v3_2.ico%22%2C%22image%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg2024.cnblogs.com%2Fblog%2F35695%2F202412%2F35695-20241201073014811-1847930772.jpg%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E2%80%94%E2%80%94Paxos%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%A8%E5%AF%BC%20-%20lzslbd%20-%20%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%9B%AD%22%2C%22belong%22%3A%22%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%9B%AD%22%2C%22belong_url%22%3Anull%2C%22desc%22%3A%22Paxos%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%A8%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E9%A2%86%E5%9F%9F%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%82%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AFPaxos%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E6%98%8E%E6%98%BE%E7%9A%84%E7%BC%BA%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%9A1.%E9%9A%BE%E4%BB%A5%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%202.%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E6%9B%B4%E9%9A%BE%E3%80%82%E6%9C%AC%E6%96%87%E8%AF%95%E5%9B%BE%E5%B8%A6%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8F%AD%E5%BC%80Paxos%E7%A5%9E%E7%A7%98%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%A2%E7%BA%B1%E3%80%82%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnblogs.com%2Flinbingdong%2Fp%2F6253479.html%22%2C%22extra%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22_serializer%22%3A%22web.editor_link_detail%22%7D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22lgP4t%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  </blockquote>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u806b91fa\&quot;" id="\&quot;u806b91fa\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue282b00d\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue282b00d\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
  <h5 data-lake-id="\&quot;XKi88\&quot;" id="\&quot;XKi88\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue99ccb7c\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue99ccb7c\&quot;">活性保证</span></h5>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u168f3bdd\&quot;" id="\&quot;u168f3bdd\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u64fdfc02\&quot;" id="\&quot;u64fdfc02\&quot;">假设有两个 Proposer 依次提出编号递增的提案，最终会陷入死循环，没有 value 被选定。（无法保证活性）</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ude17b0f2\&quot;" id="\&quot;ude17b0f2\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733481571720-dc4e7da2-b66b-4fbe-8b99-ebfd9a3a45bb.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u1c810dbe-5253-496a-bcc6-fefcb3b2170%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u860f4ff9-3604-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A777%2C%22height%22%3A265%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A808215%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1586%2C%22originHeight%22%3A540%2C%22ratio%22%3A1%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22ROPOSERP1%E5%8F%91%E5%87%BA%E7%BC%96%E5%8F%B7%E4%B8%BAM1%E7%9A%84PREPARE%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%2C%E6%94%B6%E5%88%B0%E8%BF%87%E5%8D%8A%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94.%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%22%2C%22x%22%3A27%2C%22y%22%3A18%2C%22width%22%3A876%2C%22height%22%3A37%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%98%AFP1%E5%86%8D%E6%AC%A1%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91%E5%87%BA%E7%BC%96%E5%8F%B7%E4%B8%BAM3(M3%3EM2)%E7%9A%84PREPARE%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82.%22%2C%22x%22%3A24%2C%22y%22%3A286%2C%22width%22%3A865%2C%22height%22%3A32%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22P2%E5%86%8D%E6%AC%A1%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E4%B8%80%2C%E5%8F%91%E5%87%BA%E7%BC%96%E5%8F%B7%E4%B8%BAM4(M4%3EM3)%E7%9A%84PREPARE%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%22%2C%22x%22%3A483%2C%22y%22%3A395%2C%22width%22%3A823%2C%22height%22%3A36%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22P1%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E7%9A%84%E6%97%B6%E5%80%99%2C%E5%8F%91%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84ACCEPT%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E8%A2%ABACCEPTOR%E5%BF%BD%E7%95%A5%2C%E4%BA%8E%22%2C%22x%22%3A23%2C%22y%22%3A246%2C%22width%22%3A879%2C%22height%22%3A35%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B9%9F%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E4%BA%86%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E4%B8%80%E7%9A%84%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B.%E4%BA%8E%E6%98%AFACCEPTOR%E6%89%BF%E8%AF%BA%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E7%BC%96%E5%8F%B7%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8EM2%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%90%E6%A1%88.%22%2C%22x%22%3A469%2C%22y%22%3A178%2C%22width%22%3A1042%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF...%E9%83%BD%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E4%BA%8C%2C%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89VALUE%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%89%E5%AE%9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A102%2C%22y%22%3A469%2C%22width%22%3A791%2C%22height%22%3A39%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%2CPROPOSERP2%E5%8F%91%E5%87%BA%E7%BC%96%E5%8F%B7%E4%B8%BAM2(M2%3EM1)%E7%9A%84PREPARE%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%2C%E4%B9%9F%E6%94%B6%E5%88%B0%E8%BF%87%E5%8D%8A%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94.%22%2C%22x%22%3A487%2C%22y%22%3A138%2C%22width%22%3A1049%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%BF%99%E5%8F%88%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4P2%E5%9C%A8%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E4%BA%8C%E7%9A%84ACCEPT%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E8%A2%AB%E5%BF%BD%E7%95%A5.%22%2C%22x%22%3A432%2C%22y%22%3A355%2C%22width%22%3A658%2C%22height%22%3A36%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E4%B8%80%E7%9A%84%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B.%22%2C%22x%22%3A32%2C%22y%22%3A58%2C%22width%22%3A232%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%99%B7%E5%85%A5%E6%AD%BB%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF.%22%2C%22x%22%3A20%2C%22y%22%3A467%2C%22width%22%3A216%2C%22height%22%3A42%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fcfdfa%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uea8fa1c2%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;udb7f42ea\&quot;" id="\&quot;udb7f42ea\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1a105ffb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1a105ffb\&quot;">解决方案：选取一个</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub20725e7\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub20725e7\&quot;">主 Proposer</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u25d510c7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u25d510c7\&quot;">，只有主 Proposer 才能提出提案，就可以保证Paxos算法的活性。（详情见下文）</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uc8ffd0cc\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc8ffd0cc\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;J76cl\&quot;" id="\&quot;J76cl\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u307a9bc3\&quot;" id="\&quot;u307a9bc3\&quot;">Multi Paxos</span></h4>
  <h5 data-lake-id="\&quot;Xh5v0\&quot;" id="\&quot;Xh5v0\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue33f648d\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue33f648d\&quot;">基本介绍</span></h5>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u95970682\&quot;" id="\&quot;u95970682\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0e91b3b9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0e91b3b9\&quot;">兰伯特提到的 </span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf2098a5c\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf2098a5c\&quot;">Multi-Paxos 是一种思想，不是算法</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1eb4c1eb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1eb4c1eb\&quot;">。而 Multi-Paxos 算法是一个统称，它是指基于 Multi-Paxos 思想，通过多个 Basic Paxos 实例实现一系列值的共识的算法（比如 Chubby 的 Multi-Paxos 实现、Raft 算法等）。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ub9fa9f7d\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub9fa9f7d\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4666b5c5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4666b5c5\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
  <h5 data-lake-id="\&quot;BQvjV\&quot;" id="\&quot;BQvjV\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0ac09189\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0ac09189\&quot;">问题分析</span></h5>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uf2ef3989\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf2ef3989\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u76992a20\&quot;" id="\&quot;u76992a20\&quot;">已知 Basic Paxos 是通过二阶段提交来达成共识的。在第一阶段，也就是准备阶段，接收到大多数准备响应的提议者，才能发起接受请求进入第二阶段（也就是接受阶段）。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u13ca3f4b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u13ca3f4b\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8feac7b8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8feac7b8\&quot;">如果直接通过多次执行 Basic Paxos 实例，来实现一系列值的共识，就会存在这样几个问题：</span></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;u27f1fe8f\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;uc14c211a\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u95c45b34\&quot;" id="\&quot;u95c45b34\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u399eac6c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u399eac6c\&quot;">如果多个提议者同时提交提案，可能出现因为提案编号冲突，在准备阶段没有提议者接收到大多数准备响应，协商失败，需要重新协商。</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6b5c5a6e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6b5c5a6e\&quot;">比如，一个 5 节点的集群，如果 3 个节点作为提议者同时提案，就可能发生因为没有提议者接收大多数响应（比如 1 个提议者接收到 1 个准备响应，另外 2 个提议者分别接收到 2 个准备响应）而准备失败，需要重新协商。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;uc14c211a\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u7d862b0b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7d862b0b\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucec550ee\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucec550ee\&quot;">2 轮 RPC 通讯（准备阶段和接受阶段）往返消息多、耗性能、延迟大</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u71e2c9ac\&quot;" id="\&quot;u71e2c9ac\&quot;">。你要知道，分布式系统的运行是建立在 RPC 通讯的基础之上的，因此，延迟一直是分布式系统的痛点，是需要我们在开发分布式系统时认真考虑和优化的。</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u65835bd3\&quot;" id="\&quot;u65835bd3\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h5 data-lake-id="\&quot;ofxil\&quot;" id="\&quot;ofxil\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7b955c36\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7b955c36\&quot;">解决方案</span></h5>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u20bddea8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u20bddea8\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1cb9d842\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1cb9d842\&quot;">针对问题一，可以通过引入领导者节点，作为唯一提议者，这样就不存在多个提议者同时提交提案的情况，也就不存在提案冲突的情况了：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uf0ae6d76\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf0ae6d76\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733546593768-2cffab77-b1ce-4faf-8181-84ec79ed392d.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uf889e9b3-3172-45c2-9e52-c0aca154213%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u860f4ff9-3604-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A604.5%2C%22height%22%3A367%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A156973%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A637%2C%22originHeight%22%3A387%2C%22ratio%22%3A1%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E7%AB%AF%22%2C%22x%22%3A60%2C%22y%22%3A317%2C%22width%22%3A70%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E7%AB%AF%22%2C%22x%22%3A60%2C%22y%22%3A182%2C%22width%22%3A70%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A303%2C%22y%22%3A169%2C%22width%22%3A69%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E7%AB%AF%22%2C%22x%22%3A61%2C%22y%22%3A46%2C%22width%22%3A67%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A541%2C%22y%22%3A75%2C%22width%22%3A45%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A539%2C%22y%22%3A285%2C%22width%22%3A49%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fdfdfc%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u8133c37e%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u02a03278\&quot;" id="\&quot;u02a03278\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u974d1358\&quot;" id="\&quot;u974d1358\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u49c4316f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u49c4316f\&quot;">针对问题二，</span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0980598b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0980598b\&quot;">可以采用“</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u71a3dc8c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u71a3dc8c\&quot;">当领导者处于稳定状态时，省掉准备阶段，直接进入接受阶段”</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub30247f1\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub30247f1\&quot;">这个优化机制，优化 Basic Paxos 执行。也就是说，领导者节点上，序列中的命令是最新的，不再需要通过准备请求来发现之前被大多数节点通过的提案，领导者可以独立指定提案中的值。这时，领导者在提交命令时，可以省掉准备阶段，直接进入到接受阶段：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uccfb228d\&quot;" id="\&quot;uccfb228d\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733546684773-d39e1d31-1b9f-4c83-bbc4-2293f87d6828.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u701695d7-b6ea-438f-80f4-bec0bec0bcb%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u860f4ff9-3604-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A607.5%2C%22height%22%3A349%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A150747%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A661%2C%22originHeight%22%3A380%2C%22ratio%22%3A1%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E8%AF%B7%5B%E4%BB%A5%E5%B1%B1%22%2C%22x%22%3A168%2C%22y%22%3A178%2C%22width%22%3A106%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%22%2C%22x%22%3A55%2C%22y%22%3A261%2C%22width%22%3A92%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E7%AB%AF%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%22%2C%22x%22%3A56%2C%22y%22%3A70%2C%22width%22%3A89%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A326%2C%22y%22%3A17%2C%22width%22%3A58%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%22%2C%22x%22%3A564%2C%22y%22%3A224%2C%22width%22%3A83%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A516%2C%22y%22%3A17%2C%22width%22%3A58%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%22%2C%22x%22%3A285%2C%22y%22%3A228%2C%22width%22%3A69%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E7%AB%AF%22%2C%22x%22%3A17%2C%22y%22%3A18%2C%22width%22%3A55%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%8F%90%E8%AE%AE%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A133%2C%22y%22%3A18%2C%22width%22%3A58%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23faf9f9%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u2765e203%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u354212e1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u354212e1\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4aff9207\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4aff9207\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
  <h5 data-lake-id="\&quot;nTwkd\&quot;" id="\&quot;nTwkd\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u21733d32\&quot;" id="\&quot;u21733d32\&quot;">Chubby 实现</span></h5>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u8ce262e4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8ce262e4\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub4ccf4b6\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub4ccf4b6\&quot;">兰伯特只是大概的介绍了 Multi-Paxos 思想，Chubby 则是补充细节，实现 Multi-Paxos 算法：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua69a36d6\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua69a36d6\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0584406f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0584406f\&quot;">首先，通过</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u265c1ae8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u265c1ae8\&quot;">引入主节点</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u80b9b095\&quot;" id="\&quot;u80b9b095\&quot;">，实现了兰伯特提到的领导者（Leader）节点的特性。也就是说，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1c72d3be\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1c72d3be\&quot;">主节点作为唯一提议者</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u92223c09\&quot;" id="\&quot;u92223c09\&quot;">，这样就不存在多个提议者同时提交提案的情况，也就不存在提案冲突的情况了。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u5a4c585b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5a4c585b\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue46a730c\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue46a730c\&quot;">另外，在 Chubby 中，主节点是通过执行 Basic Paxos 算法，进行投票选举产生的，并且在运行过程中，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub31e0dd0\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub31e0dd0\&quot;">主节点会通过不断续租的方式来延长租期（Lease）</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u49aadb40\&quot;" id="\&quot;u49aadb40\&quot;">。比如在实际场景中，几天内都是同一个节点作为主节点。如果主节点故障了，那么其他的节点又会投票选举出新的主节点，也就是说</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u97d2d722\&quot;" id="\&quot;u97d2d722\&quot;">主节点是一直存在的，而且是唯一的。</span></strong></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u30bad4f1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u30bad4f1\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf5802326\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf5802326\&quot;">其次，在 Chubby 中实现了兰伯特提到的，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u23779d40\&quot;" id="\&quot;u23779d40\&quot;">“当领导者处于稳定状态时，省掉准备阶段，直接进入接受阶段”</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua059b4fe\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua059b4fe\&quot;">这个优化机制。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;udb7c8c06\&quot;" id="\&quot;udb7c8c06\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0c677b5b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0c677b5b\&quot;">最后，在 Chubby 中，实现了</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u318f19b6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u318f19b6\&quot;">成员变更（Group membership）</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u67ed3357\&quot;" id="\&quot;u67ed3357\&quot;">，以此保证节点变更的时候集群的平稳运行。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u90d4ddcb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u90d4ddcb\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u80a36f86\&quot;" id="\&quot;u80a36f86\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u94dfd5a4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u94dfd5a4\&quot;">注意：</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5cf8f474\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5cf8f474\&quot;">如何理解领导者处于稳定状态？</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ubd40ff2c\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubd40ff2c\&quot;"> 领导者节点上，序列中的命令是最新的，不再需要通过准备请求来发现之前被大多数节点通过的提案，领导者可以独立指定提案中的值。具体来说，准备阶段的意义，是发现接受者节点上，已经通过的提案的值。如果在所有接受者节点上，都没有已经通过的提案，这时领导者就可以直接指定提案的值，那么准备阶段就没有意义了，也就可以省掉了。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ue2dd10b8\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue2dd10b8\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u86c9107c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u86c9107c\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5a3fc6d6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5a3fc6d6\&quot;">在 Chubby 中，为了实现了强一致性，读操作也只能在主节点上执行。</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua1ba18d3\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua1ba18d3\&quot;"> 也就是说，只要数据写入成功，之后所有的客户端读到的数据都是一致的。具体的过程如下：</span></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;uc9c42cf6\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;ucd78bc37\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u342e3ba0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u342e3ba0\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5a2472fc\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5a2472fc\&quot;">所有的读请求和写请求都由主节点来处理。当主节点从客户端接收到写请求后，作为提议者，执行 Basic Paxos 实例，将数据发送给所有的节点，并且在大多数的服务器接受了这个写请求之后，再响应给客户端成功：</span></li>
  </ul>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ud786e0e4\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud786e0e4\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-indent:" 2em\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733547731108-f22978fe-f291-40d8-8f2a-baa2108e5111.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uad92db20-bdd3-4efe-a028-91f6bb86e5a%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u860f4ff9-3604-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A578%2C%22height%22%3A308%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A140782%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A656%2C%22originHeight%22%3A349%2C%22ratio%22%3A1%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%222%E5%86%99%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%22%2C%22x%22%3A346%2C%22y%22%3A135%2C%22width%22%3A107%2C%22height%22%3A-32%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%BB%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A318%2C%22y%22%3A164%2C%22width%22%3A60%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221.%E5%86%99%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%22%2C%22x%22%3A135%2C%22y%22%3A135%2C%22width%22%3A68%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%224%2C%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%22%2C%22x%22%3A239%2C%22y%22%3A206%2C%22width%22%3A61%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AE%83%E7%9C%8B%E5%8A%9F%22%2C%22x%22%3A436%2C%22y%22%3A184%2C%22width%22%3A64%2C%22height%22%3A56%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E7%AB%AF%22%2C%22x%22%3A48%2C%22y%22%3A176%2C%22width%22%3A64%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%2C%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%22%2C%22x%22%3A488%2C%22y%22%3A126%2C%22width%22%3A54%2C%22height%22%3A-4%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%223.%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%22%2C%22x%22%3A467%2C%22y%22%3A267%2C%22width%22%3A59%2C%22height%22%3A50%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A558%2C%22y%22%3A275%2C%22width%22%3A42%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A557%2C%22y%22%3A53%2C%22width%22%3A43%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fafafa%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u0da1bc75%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;u9eccbfe9\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u0afb3405\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;uac56632c\&quot;" id="\&quot;uac56632c\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uebed68a8\&quot;" id="\&quot;uebed68a8\&quot;">当主节点接收到读请求后，处理就比较简单了，主节点只需要查询本地数据，然后返回给客户端就可以了：</span></li>
  </ul>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u8cf2f7fc\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8cf2f7fc\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-indent:" 2em\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733547759624-ed4d925f-cfe8-4a03-b996-a68e6437a1da.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u66dca626-91d2-4aea-8d73-7371c49218a%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u860f4ff9-3604-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A572%2C%22height%22%3A298%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A114740%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A660%2C%22originHeight%22%3A344%2C%22ratio%22%3A1%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%BB%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A316%2C%22y%22%3A163%2C%22width%22%3A64%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E7%AB%AF%22%2C%22x%22%3A47%2C%22y%22%3A175%2C%22width%22%3A67%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221.%E8%AF%BB%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%22%2C%22x%22%3A138%2C%22y%22%3A134%2C%22width%22%3A68%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%222.%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%22%2C%22x%22%3A244%2C%22y%22%3A204%2C%22width%22%3A56%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A559%2C%22y%22%3A51%2C%22width%22%3A40%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A560%2C%22y%22%3A275%2C%22width%22%3A39%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fcfcfc%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u85088d6f%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u481bcd36\&quot;" id="\&quot;u481bcd36\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub1296f08\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub1296f08\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
  <blockquote data-lake-id="\&quot;uf65c14a4\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf65c14a4\&quot;">
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u87d1503b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u87d1503b\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7eb9638f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7eb9638f\&quot;">参考文章：</span></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u17ac8788\&quot;" id="\&quot;u17ac8788\&quot;">
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;bookmarkInline\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22mode%22%3A%22title%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2F100046101%2F202772%2F%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2F100046101%2F202772%2F%22%2C%22detail%22%3A%7B%22icon%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2Ffavicon.ico%22%2C%22image%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic001.geekbang.org%2Fresource%2Fimage%2F1f%2Ffe%2F1f986c063f3bfe2547e14447d6230bfe.jpg%22%2C%22title%22%3A%2206%20%7C%20Paxos%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9AMulti-Paxos%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E6%98%AF%E7%BB%9F%E7%A7%B0%22%2C%22belong%22%3A%22%E6%9E%81%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%B7%B2%E5%AE%8C%E7%BB%93%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E9%99%90%E6%97%B6%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB%22%2C%22belong_url%22%3Anull%2C%22desc%22%3A%22Multi-Paxos%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8EMulti-Paxos%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AABasic%20Paxos%E5%AE%9E%E4%BE%8B%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E4%B8%80%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E5%80%BC%E5%85%B1%E8%AF%86%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E3%80%82%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2F100046101%2F202772%2F%22%2C%22extra%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22_serializer%22%3A%22web.editor_link_detail%22%7D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22tUeD0%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ubf9efbcc\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubf9efbcc\&quot;">
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;bookmarkInline\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22mode%22%3A%22title%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzI4NDMyNTU2Mw%3D%3D%26mid%3D2247483695%26idx%3D1%26sn%3D91ea422913fc62579e020e941d1d059e%26chksm%3Debfc62fbdc8bebed551c2a041bb37bcaab836c4b2ca8e575d418f1e24459459c1c16faf70d06%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzI4NDMyNTU2Mw%3D%3D%26mid%3D2247483695%26idx%3D1%26sn%3D91ea422913fc62579e020e941d1d059e%26chksm%3Debfc62fbdc8bebed551c2a041bb37bcaab836c4b2ca8e575d418f1e24459459c1c16faf70d06%22%2C%22detail%22%3A%7B%22icon%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fres.wx.qq.com%2Fa%2Fwx_fed%2Fassets%2Fres%2FNTI4MWU5.ico%22%2C%22image%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz%2FUqFrHRLeCAnty2ANWDEaHx5JN1cTN1ogP6EAW2OX1CdADStmqzM0zib4WROay6LP9q3t9boXJ7vlvurFicTiaIGpg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E8%87%AA%E7%A0%94%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E7%BA%A7paxos%E7%B1%BB%E5%BA%93PhxPaxos%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D%22%2C%22belong%22%3A%22%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%85%AC%E4%BC%97%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%22%2C%22belong_url%22%3Anull%2C%22desc%22%3A%22%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E9%87%8D%E7%A3%85%E5%BC%80%E6%BA%90%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E7%BA%A7paxos%E7%B1%BB%E5%BA%93PhxPaxos%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%AC%E6%96%87%E7%94%A8%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%A3%E5%90%BB%E5%90%91%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8DPhxPaxos%E8%83%8C%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E6%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%86%E8%8A%82%E3%80%82%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzI4NDMyNTU2Mw%3D%3D%26mid%3D2247483695%26idx%3D1%26sn%3D91ea422913fc62579e020e941d1d059e%26chksm%3Debfc62fbdc8bebed551c2a041bb37bcaab836c4b2ca8e575d418f1e24459459c1c16faf70d06%22%2C%22extra%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22_serializer%22%3A%22web.editor_link_detail%22%7D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22X9VDF%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  </blockquote>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u04820492\&quot;" id="\&quot;u04820492\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua67fdfdb\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua67fdfdb\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
  <h3 data-lake-id="\&quot;KhZjl\&quot;" id="\&quot;KhZjl\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uee921f0f\&quot;" id="\&quot;uee921f0f\&quot;">Raft</span></h3>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;an8HO\&quot;" id="\&quot;an8HO\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc814a68d\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc814a68d\&quot;">基本介绍</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u17345a03\&quot;" id="\&quot;u17345a03\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue78b8fa1\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue78b8fa1\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">Raft 算法属于 Multi-Paxos 算法，它是在兰伯特 Multi-Paxos 思想的基础上，做了一些简化和限制，比如增加了日志必须是连续的，只支持领导者、跟随者和候选人三种状态，在理解和算法实现上都相对容易许多。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u65197cda\&quot;" id="\&quot;u65197cda\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u752b1e63\&quot;" id="\&quot;u752b1e63\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ub861f976\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub861f976\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u77353e28\&quot;" id="\&quot;u77353e28\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0)\"="">从本质上说，Raft 算法是通过一切以领导者为准的方式，实现一系列值的共识和各节点日志的一致。</span></strong></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uf9c89034\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf9c89034\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6f7874d1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6f7874d1\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <blockquote data-lake-id="\&quot;u5ec9db53\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5ec9db53\&quot;">
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ubca63536\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubca63536\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uace64be2\&quot;" id="\&quot;uace64be2\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">Raft 动画演示：</span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;bookmarkInline\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22mode%22%3A%22title%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesecretlivesofdata.com%2Fraft%2F%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesecretlivesofdata.com%2Fraft%2F%22%2C%22detail%22%3A%7B%22icon%22%3Anull%2C%22title%22%3A%22Raft%22%2C%22belong%22%3A%22The%20Secret%20Lives%20of%20Data%22%2C%22belong_url%22%3Anull%2C%22desc%22%3Anull%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesecretlivesofdata.com%2Fraft%2F%22%2C%22extra%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22_serializer%22%3A%22web.editor_link_detail%22%7D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22FW9mh%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  </blockquote>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u77fa11f2\&quot;" id="\&quot;u77fa11f2\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0a0da4c2\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0a0da4c2\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;zFBNU\&quot;" id="\&quot;zFBNU\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2b462082\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2b462082\&quot;">成员身份</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u86d23c2d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u86d23c2d\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4a44dd45\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4a44dd45\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">成员身份，又叫做服务器节点状态，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u674fdaa9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u674fdaa9\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0)\"="">Raft 算法支持领导者（Leader）、跟随者（Follower）和候选人（Candidate） 3 种状态。</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u094e9ff0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u094e9ff0\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">为了方便讲解，我们使用不同的图形表示不同的状态。在任何时候，每一个服务器节点都处于这 3 个状态中的 1 个。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u1e42c70a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1e42c70a\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733555895904-af29ba7e-27d5-4ae3-b0ed-23df40f87df3.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uabd79f67-0360-488a-adc9-6da8c8e83d7%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ubb9d1f1b-a295-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A566.5%2C%22height%22%3A148%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A73091%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A663%2C%22originHeight%22%3A173%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%B7%9F%E9%9A%8F%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A45%2C%22y%22%3A137%2C%22width%22%3A71%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%80%99%E9%80%89%E4%BA%BA%22%2C%22x%22%3A296%2C%22y%22%3A138%2C%22width%22%3A70%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A543%2C%22y%22%3A137%2C%22width%22%3A72%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23c7c7c5%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u37f79186%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;u7f298795\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u3b252527\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u6d164702\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6d164702\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc1d8d2f9\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc1d8d2f9\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">跟随者：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6c19d336\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6c19d336\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">就相当于普通群众，默默地接收和处理来自领导者的消息，当等待领导者心跳信息超时的时候，就主动站出来，推荐自己当候选人。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;u3b252527\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ub587f630\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub587f630\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uab27f1a2\&quot;" id="\&quot;uab27f1a2\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">候选人：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u09642766\&quot;" id="\&quot;u09642766\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">候选人将向其他节点发送请求投票（RequestVote）RPC 消息，通知其他节点来投票，如果赢得了</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue114064a\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue114064a\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">大多数</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6416c678\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6416c678\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">选票，就晋升当领导者。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;u3b252527\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ub5e1ba8f\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub5e1ba8f\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u75132458\&quot;" id="\&quot;u75132458\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">领导者：一切以领导为准，</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u939df2d5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u939df2d5\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">主要工作内容就是 3 部分，处理写请求、管理日志复制和不断地发送心跳信息，通知其他节点“我是领导者，我还活着，你们现在不要发起新的选举，找个新领导者来替代我。”</span></li>
  </ul>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uf41f4193\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf41f4193\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf5fe6e12\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf5fe6e12\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0)\"="">注意：Raft 算法是</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u39710b9a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u39710b9a\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0)\"="">强领导者模型，集群中只能有一个领导者。</span></strong></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u3a4fd079\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3a4fd079\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;na5Bg\&quot;" id="\&quot;na5Bg\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua8f68648\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua8f68648\&quot;">领导选举</span></h4>
  <h5 data-lake-id="\&quot;gSu0V\&quot;" id="\&quot;gSu0V\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u86111b85\&quot;" id="\&quot;u86111b85\&quot;">相关概念</span></h5>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u09f68e25\&quot;" id="\&quot;u09f68e25\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud47d1215\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud47d1215\&quot;">在了解领导选举之前，需要知道各个节点间如何通信，什么是任期，随机超时时间的概念：</span></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;u00520340\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u79ff3c69\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u8add9d74\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8add9d74\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u66f466ca\&quot;" id="\&quot;u66f466ca\&quot;">节点通信：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u68f1eeb2\&quot;" id="\&quot;u68f1eeb2\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">在 Raft 算法中，服务器节点间的沟通联络采用的是远程过程调用（RPC），在领导者选举中，需要用到这样两类的 RPC：</span></li>
  </ol>
  <ul list="\&quot;u216e3038\&quot;" data-lake-indent="\&quot;1\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u778c98a5\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u5e3d9121\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5e3d9121\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2374b95e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2374b95e\&quot;">请求投票（RequestVote）RPC</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u718e78f8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u718e78f8\&quot;">，是由候选人在选举期间发起，通知各节点进行投票</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;u778c98a5\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u48c1ba66\&quot;" id="\&quot;u48c1ba66\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7ba40ca5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7ba40ca5\&quot;">日志复制（AppendEntries）RPC</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7248e317\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7248e317\&quot;">，是由领导者发起，用来复制日志和提供心跳消息</span></li>
  </ul>
  <ol list="\&quot;u00520340\&quot;" start="\&quot;2\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u79ff3c69\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u1edbe6a9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1edbe6a9\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufa098e01\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufa098e01\&quot;">任期：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u62ed2990\&quot;" id="\&quot;u62ed2990\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(5,="" 7,="" 59)\"="">每一个任期（Term）可以看作是</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4fd2d380\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4fd2d380\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(5,="" 7,="" 59)\"="">一个连续的时间段</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0693f6e9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0693f6e9\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(5,="" 7,="" 59)\"="">，Raft 集群在这期间有可能会有一个领导者被选出，也可能没有（如果选举失败）。任期</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc6791d81\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc6791d81\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(5,="" 7,="" 59)\"="">用一个整数来标识，并随时间递增</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf0029868\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf0029868\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(5,="" 7,="" 59)\"="">。</span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2c5c3fa0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2c5c3fa0\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">任期编号是随着选举的举行而变化的。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;u79ff3c69\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u39cb2bda\&quot;" id="\&quot;u39cb2bda\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7052f13c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7052f13c\&quot;">随机超时时间：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud281c6a7\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud281c6a7\&quot;">在 Raft 算法的选举中，常出现未达到指定票数，选举无效，需要重新选举的情况。Raft 使用随机选举超时时间的方法，把超时时间都分散开来，在大多数情况下只有一个服务器节点先发起选举，而不是同时发起选举，这样就能减少因</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u11ab9af1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u11ab9af1\&quot;">选票瓜分（Split Vote）</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u99ec8670\&quot;" id="\&quot;u99ec8670\&quot;">导致选举失败的情况。需要强调的是，在 Raft 算法中，随机超时时间是有 2 种含义的：</span></li>
  </ol>
  <ol list="\&quot;u00520340\&quot;" data-lake-indent="\&quot;1\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u79ff3c69\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u1dca46b6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1dca46b6\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf6bd8c78\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf6bd8c78\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">跟随者</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2e82429a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2e82429a\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">等待领导者心跳信息超时的时间间隔</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc8d37e9c\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc8d37e9c\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">，是随机的</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;u79ff3c69\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ucfcf9487\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucfcf9487\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u26745945\&quot;" id="\&quot;u26745945\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">如果候选人在一个随机时间间隔内，没有赢得过半票数，那么选举无效了，然后候选人发起新一轮的选举，也就是说，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2aeeb9bc\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2aeeb9bc\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">等待选举超时的时间间隔，是随机的</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u15dcade1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u15dcade1\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">。</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u70a81f4e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u70a81f4e\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufad72e0a\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufad72e0a\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
  <h5 data-lake-id="\&quot;HbtzB\&quot;" id="\&quot;HbtzB\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0ec5efa4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0ec5efa4\&quot;">选举过程</span></h5>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ue0162eb4\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue0162eb4\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4e60521b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4e60521b\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">以图例的形式演示一个典型的领导者选举过程。三个成员是如何选举出来领导者：</span></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;uc11ae046\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u5a2fc31f\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u077d5a31\&quot;" id="\&quot;u077d5a31\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u870ad6b9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u870ad6b9\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">在初始状态下，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u234b4744\&quot;" id="\&quot;u234b4744\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">集群中所有的节点都是跟随者的状态</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u00143543\&quot;" id="\&quot;u00143543\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">。</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u04ac44a1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u04ac44a1\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-indent:" 2em\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733556304819-49bb6889-d2e7-4904-b026-8192bbcfa7bf.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u42d16def-4855-46d9-b219-34c5e423e23%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ubb9d1f1b-a295-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A471.5%2C%22height%22%3A402%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A188726%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A635%2C%22originHeight%22%3A541%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%B6%85%E6%97%B6%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%3A300S%22%2C%22x%22%3A227%2C%22y%22%3A352%2C%22width%22%3A194%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%B6%85%E6%97%B6%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%3A150S%22%2C%22x%22%3A32%2C%22y%22%3A106%2C%22width%22%3A194%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%B6%85%E6%97%B6%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%3A200S%22%2C%22x%22%3A422%2C%22y%22%3A103%2C%22width%22%3A194%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%BB%BB%E6%9C%9F%E7%BC%96%E5%8F%B7%3A0%22%2C%22x%22%3A227%2C%22y%22%3A317%2C%22width%22%3A142%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%BB%BB%E6%9C%9F%E7%BC%96%E5%8F%B7%3A0%22%2C%22x%22%3A33%2C%22y%22%3A71%2C%22width%22%3A137%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%BB%BB%E6%9C%9F%E7%BC%96%E5%8F%B7%3A0%22%2C%22x%22%3A423%2C%22y%22%3A69%2C%22width%22%3A136%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A87%2C%22y%22%3A23%2C%22width%22%3A87%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%B7%9F%E9%9A%8F%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A278%2C%22y%22%3A441%2C%22width%22%3A88%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A479%2C%22y%22%3A22%2C%22width%22%3A83%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%B7%9F%E9%9A%8F%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A473%2C%22y%22%3A198%2C%22width%22%3A89%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%B7%9F%E9%9A%8F%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A82%2C%22y%22%3A197%2C%22width%22%3A90%2C%22height%22%3A32%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A286%2C%22y%22%3A270%2C%22width%22%3A80%2C%22height%22%3A32%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f8f8f8%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uf613def8%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;u11752c28\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;ub68c9902\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u991c2b05\&quot;" id="\&quot;u991c2b05\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;udecb3299\&quot;" id="\&quot;udecb3299\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">Raft 算法实现了</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4b0b291f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4b0b291f\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">随机超时时间</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue806e28f\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue806e28f\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">的特性。每个节点等待领导者节点心跳信息的超时时间间隔是随机的（150ms-300ms 之间）。通过上面的图片可以看到，集群中没有领导者，而节点 A 的等待超时时间最小（150ms），它会最先因为没有等到领导者的心跳信息，发生超时。</span></li>
  </ul>
  <ol list="\&quot;uf0e63c60\&quot;" start="\&quot;2\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;uca765d24\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u97d8c496\&quot;" id="\&quot;u97d8c496\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf6028c58\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf6028c58\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">此时节点 A 就增加自己的任期编号，并推举自己为候选人，先给自己投上一张选票，然后向其他节点发送请求投票 RPC 消息，请它们选举自己为领导者。</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ucb02807c\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucb02807c\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-indent:" 2em\"="">
