2%3A37%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22Y-%22%2C%22x%22%3A223%2C%22y%22%3A399%2C%22width%22%3A35%2C%22height%22%3A14%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%222%22%2C%22x%22%3A178%2C%22y%22%3A69%2C%22width%22%3A15%2C%22height%22%3A16%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B9%89%E4%BA%8C-2%22%2C%22x%22%3A280%2C%22y%22%3A401%2C%22width%22%3A32%2C%22height%22%3A12%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%222%22%2C%22x%22%3A290%2C%22y%22%3A101%2C%22width%22%3A15%2C%22height%22%3A12%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%223%22%2C%22x%22%3A346%2C%22y%22%3A168%2C%22width%22%3A23%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%222%22%2C%22x%22%3A289%2C%22y%22%3A166%2C%22width%22%3A20%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%223%22%2C%22x%22%3A346%2C%22y%22%3A97%2C%22width%22%3A21%2C%22height%22%3A16%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fcfcfb%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u7480ccf1%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;ucba3f694\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u261d06ed\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u003df661\&quot;" id="\&quot;u003df661\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4da77bd8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4da77bd8\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">指令：一条由客户端请求指定的、状态机需要执行的指令。你可以将指令理解成客户端指定的数据。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;u261d06ed\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u7d23b0ae\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7d23b0ae\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3178884d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3178884d\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">索引值：日志项对应的整数索引值。其实就是用来标识日志项的，是一个连续的、单调递增的整数号码。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;u261d06ed\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u3c08d5b6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3c08d5b6\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u08f1f816\&quot;" id="\&quot;u08f1f816\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">任期编号：创建这条日志项的领导者的任期编号。</span></li>
  </ul>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ud5fefb48\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud5fefb48\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h5 data-lake-id="\&quot;SRnIx\&quot;" id="\&quot;SRnIx\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ubd6a0433\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubd6a0433\&quot;">复制过程</span></h5>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uc61c8523\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc61c8523\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc67e3ab5\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc67e3ab5\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">可以把 Raft 的日志复制理解成一个优化后的二阶段提交（将二阶段优化成了一阶段），减少了一半的往返消息，也就是降低了一半的消息延迟。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u0e09900c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0e09900c\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf75ca537\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf75ca537\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ubcddf91b\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubcddf91b\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2c7d67f8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2c7d67f8\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">大致过程如下：</span></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;u5fa65ed5\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;uc60f3dfa\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;uaec3f80e\&quot;" id="\&quot;uaec3f80e\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud0abe974\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud0abe974\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">首先，领导者进入第一阶段，通过日志复制（AppendEntries）RPC 消息，将日志项复制到集群其他节点上。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;uc60f3dfa\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u079965ce\&quot;" id="\&quot;u079965ce\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2c434041\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2c434041\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">接着，如果领导者接收到</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u48a8f316\&quot;" id="\&quot;u48a8f316\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">大多数</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u08496546\&quot;" id="\&quot;u08496546\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">的“复制成功”响应后，它将日志项应用到它的状态机，并返回成功给客户端。如果领导者没有接收到大多数的“复制成功”响应，那么就返回错误给客户端。</span></li>
  </ul>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u3ee6cc7f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3ee6cc7f\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub24013ce\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub24013ce\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u7a9733d6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7a9733d6\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub75fc558\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub75fc558\&quot;">注意：</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8cf441d5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8cf441d5\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">领导者将日志项应用到它的状态机，不会直接通知跟随者应用日志项。</span></strong></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u93a9f310\&quot;" id="\&quot;u93a9f310\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u81381ec4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u81381ec4\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">这是 Raft 中的一个优化，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9332d55d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9332d55d\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u90bd7d8f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u90bd7d8f\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">因为</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub5675f85\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub5675f85\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">领导者的日志复制 RPC 消息或心跳消息，包含了当前最大的，将会被提交（Commit）的日志项索引值</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc3ad029d\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc3ad029d\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">。所以通过日志复制 RPC 消息或心跳消息，跟随者就可以知道领导者的日志提交位置信息。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u65cfe2df\&quot;" id="\&quot;u65cfe2df\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0c48a474\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0c48a474\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">因此，当其他节点接受领导者的心跳消息，或者新的日志复制 RPC 消息后，就会将这条日志项应用到它的状态机。而这个优化，降低了处理客户端请求的延迟，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub113464d\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub113464d\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">将二阶段提交优化为了一段提交，降低了一半的消息延迟</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u911a58cc\&quot;" id="\&quot;u911a58cc\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u552e34b1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u552e34b1\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ue3830b95\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue3830b95\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u371c15e5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u371c15e5\&quot;">具体过程如下图：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u90f48d87\&quot;" id="\&quot;u90f48d87\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733560654876-10ef6099-8be2-4b3e-8e94-c1838df82db9.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u8e7e3909-0a4e-45ee-987a-c41674d705b%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ubb9d1f1b-a295-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A611.5%2C%22height%22%3A271%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A138285%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A673%2C%22originHeight%22%3A298%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%225%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%22%2C%22x%22%3A553%2C%22y%22%3A232%2C%22width%22%3A104%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%223%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%22%2C%22x%22%3A229%2C%22y%22%3A43%2C%22width%22%3A102%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%222.%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6RPC%22%2C%22x%22%3A310%2C%22y%22%3A101%2C%22width%22%3A98%2C%22height%22%3A-29%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%222.%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6RPC%22%2C%22x%22%3A314%2C%22y%22%3A164%2C%22width%22%3A97%2C%22height%22%3A87%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22.%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E7%AB%AF%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%22%2C%22x%22%3A96%2C%22y%22%3A115%2C%22width%22%3A82%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%224.%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A145%2C%22y%22%3A173%2C%22width%22%3A109%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%225.%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%22%2C%22x%22%3A550%2C%22y%22%3A63%2C%22width%22%3A108%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E7%AB%AF%22%2C%22x%22%3A32%2C%22y%22%3A148%2C%22width%22%3A55%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%B7%9F%E9%9A%8F%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A440%2C%22y%22%3A232%2C%22width%22%3A55%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A251%2C%22y%22%3A138%2C%22width%22%3A55%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%B7%9F%E9%9A%8F%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A440%2C%22y%22%3A48%2C%22width%22%3A56%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23faf9f9%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uf2e3fb52%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;u8104a727\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u2ac155e3\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ucae194e9\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucae194e9\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u006d48e9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u006d48e9\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">接收到客户端请求后，领导者基于客户端请求中的指令，创建一个新日志项，并附加到本地日志中。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;u2ac155e3\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;uf3af9a92\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf3af9a92\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6d5ee8c8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6d5ee8c8\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">领导者通过日志复制 RPC，将新的日志项复制到其他的服务器。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;u2ac155e3\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ucf4408bb\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucf4408bb\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6ac5d1ad\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6ac5d1ad\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">当领导者将日志项，成功复制到大多数的服务器上的时候，领导者会将这条日志项应用到它的状态机中。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;u2ac155e3\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u8a200423\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8a200423\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u84d65e99\&quot;" id="\&quot;u84d65e99\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">领导者将执行的结果返回给客户端。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;u2ac155e3\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u5908f44c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5908f44c\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u40595af7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u40595af7\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">当跟随者接收到心跳信息，或者新的日志复制 RPC 消息后，如果跟随者发现领导者已经提交了某条日志项，而它还没应用，那么跟随者就将这条日志项应用到本地的状态机中。</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u4244e2a1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4244e2a1\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1503fc53\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1503fc53\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ub685c29a\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub685c29a\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc1e1cb9a\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc1e1cb9a\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">注意：这是一个理想状态下的日志复制过程。在实际环境中，复制日志的时候，你可能会遇到进程崩溃、服务器宕机等问题，这些问题会导致日志不一致。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u5e0047b9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5e0047b9\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h5 data-lake-id="\&quot;SQSSQ\&quot;" id="\&quot;SQSSQ\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1ebc7016\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1ebc7016\&quot;">实现一致</span></h5>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ucc9b947c\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucc9b947c\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u044ea00f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u044ea00f\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">在 Raft 算法中，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue7310b5f\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue7310b5f\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">领导者通过强制跟随者直接复制自己的日志项，处理不一致日志</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub5e27275\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub5e27275\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">。也就是说，Raft 是通过以领导者的日志为准，来实现各节点日志的一致的。具体有 2 个步骤：</span></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;ue50976e7\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u04d39e4f\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u11f8afba\&quot;" id="\&quot;u11f8afba\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9fd36eb9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9fd36eb9\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">首先，领导者通过日志复制 RPC 的一致性检查，找到跟随者节点上，与自己相同日志项的最大索引值。也就是说，这个索引值之前的日志，领导者和跟随者是一致的，之后的日志是不一致的了。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;u04d39e4f\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;uaeda5d80\&quot;" id="\&quot;uaeda5d80\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub0c607c1\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub0c607c1\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">然后，领导者强制跟随者更新覆盖的不一致日志项，实现日志的一致。</span></li>
  </ul>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uc0917a10\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc0917a10\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u40175b50\&quot;" id="\&quot;u40175b50\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u59de448e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u59de448e\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue679414a\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue679414a\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">详细地走一遍这个过程（为了方便演示，我们引入 2 个新变量）：</span></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;u9bf586ce\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u7b34913e\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;uf3772d46\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf3772d46\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc9ec8423\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc9ec8423\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">PrevLogEntry</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9632eec4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9632eec4\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">：表示当前要复制的日志项，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u88d98a8f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u88d98a8f\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">前面一条日志项的索引值</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc8ada653\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc8ada653\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">。比如在下图中，如果领导者将索引值为 8 的日志项发送给跟随者，那么此时 PrevLogEntry 值为 7。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;u7b34913e\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u644929af\&quot;" id="\&quot;u644929af\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uda00ea0d\&quot;" id="\&quot;uda00ea0d\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">PrevLogTerm</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8115e577\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8115e577\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">：表示当前要复制的日志项，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ubf9496c3\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubf9496c3\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">前面一条日志项的任期编号</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ueb38477b\&quot;" id="\&quot;ueb38477b\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">。比如在下图中，如果领导者将索引值为 8 的日志项发送给跟随者，那么此时 PrevLogTerm 值为 4。</span></li>
  </ul>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ue37d7414\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue37d7414\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4d260067\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4d260067\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">具体过程如下图：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uef8ab623\&quot;" id="\&quot;uef8ab623\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733561041565-f469f284-59a6-4120-b900-077a0ea135b0.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uc191f315-683f-4983-86e8-884c232fce7%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ubb9d1f1b-a295-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A548.5%2C%22height%22%3A528%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A343943%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A655%2C%22originHeight%22%3A631%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%225%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6RPC%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%22%2C%22x%22%3A135%2C%22y%22%3A546%2C%22width%22%3A318%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22TLOG(%3AX-4%2C...%22%2C%22x%22%3A128%2C%22y%22%3A187%2C%22width%22%3A117%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%223LOG%5B%5D%3AX%3C-5%2C..%22%2C%22x%22%3A129%2C%22y%22%3A339%2C%22width%22%3A115%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22PREVLOGTERN%3A4%22%2C%22x%22%3A129%2C%22y%22%3A236%2C%22width%22%3A114%2C%22height%22%3A16%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22PREVLOGENFRY%3AB%22%2C%22x%22%3A129%2C%22y%22%3A365%2C%22width%22%3A113%2C%22height%22%3A16%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22PREVLOGTERKN%3A3%22%2C%22x%22%3A129%2C%22y%22%3A388%2C%22width%22%3A111%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22PREVLOGENTRY%3A7%22%2C%22x%22%3A128%2C%22y%22%3A212%2C%22width%22%3A113%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A34%2C%22y%22%3A279%2C%22width%22%3A63%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A33%2C%22y%22%3A560%2C%22width%22%3A65%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A575%2C%22y%22%3A55%2C%22width%22%3A61%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%B7%9F%E9%9A%8F%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A494%2C%22y%22%3A561%2C%22width%22%3A66%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%B7%9F%E9%9A%8F%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A494%2C%22y%22%3A280%2C%22width%22%3A66%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A35%2C%22y%22%3A432%2C%22width%22%3A62%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22F.SUCCESS%22%2C%22x%22%3A335%2C%22y%22%3A437%2C%22width%22%3A67%2C%22height%22%3A12%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%B7%9F%E9%9A%8F%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A498%2C%22y%22%3A433%2C%22width%22%3A62%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%B7%9F%E9%9A%8F%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A574%2C%22y%22%3A126%2C%22width%22%3A63%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%222.FAILURE%22%2C%22x%22%3A331%2C%22y%22%3A282%2C%22width%22%3A72%2C%22height%22%3A16%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22X%3C-5%22%2C%22x%22%3A432%2C%22y%22%3A71%2C%22width%22%3A43%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22X%3C-4%22%2C%22x%22%3A501%2C%22y%22%3A72%2C%22width%22%3A41%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22Y%3C-7%22%2C%22x%22%3A371%2C%22y%22%3A142%2C%22width%22%3A39%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22X%3C-3%22%2C%22x%22%3A38%2C%22y%22%3A142%2C%22width%22%3A42%2C%22height%22%3A14%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22X%3C-2%22%2C%22x%22%3A238%2C%22y%22%3A142%2C%22width%22%3A39%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22X%3C-0%22%2C%22x%22%3A301%2C%22y%22%3A71%2C%22width%22%3A42%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22X%3C-0%22%2C%22x%22%3A306%2C%22y%22%3A143%2C%22width%22%3A39%2C%22height%22%3A14%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22Y%3C-Q%22%2C%22x%22%3A169%2C%22y%22%3A142%2C%22width%22%3A44%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22Y%3C-Q%22%2C%22x%22%3A169%2C%22y%22%3A71%2C%22width%22%3A43%2C%22height%22%3A16%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22X%3C-3%22%2C%22x%22%3A36%2C%22y%22%3A71%2C%22width%22%3A45%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22V%3C-1%22%2C%22x%22%3A104%2C%22y%22%3A72%2C%22width%22%3A42%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22X%3C-2%22%2C%22x%22%3A235%2C%22y%22%3A72%2C%22width%22%3A42%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22Y%3C-1%22%2C%22x%22%3A103%2C%22y%22%3A142%2C%22width%22%3A43%2C%22height%22%3A16%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22Y%3C-7%22%2C%22x%22%3A366%2C%22y%22%3A71%2C%22width%22%3A43%2C%22height%22%3A16%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22Y%3C-5%22%2C%22x%22%3A435%2C%22y%22%3A142%2C%22width%22%3A43%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%224%22%2C%22x%22%3A510%2C%22y%22%3A47%2C%22width%22%3A23%2C%22height%22%3A12%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%224%22%2C%22x%22%3A446%2C%22y%22%3A47%2C%22width%22%3A18%2C%22height%22%3A12%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%223%22%2C%22x%22%3A378%2C%22y%22%3A45%2C%22width%22%3A21%2C%22height%22%3A16%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fdfdfb%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uaedcfbe8%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;uaf1a35f2\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;ub0361ccd\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u5080970e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5080970e\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u77fce640\&quot;" id="\&quot;u77fce640\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">领导者通过日志复制 RPC 消息，发送当前最新日志项到跟随者（为了演示方便，假设当前需要复制的日志项是最新的），这个消息的 PrevLogEntry 值为 7，PrevLogTerm 值为 4。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;ub0361ccd\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u57c21c76\&quot;" id="\&quot;u57c21c76\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue63668fd\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue63668fd\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">如果跟随者在它的日志中，找不到与 PrevLogEntry 值为 7、PrevLogTerm 值为 4 的日志项，也就是说它的日志和领导者的不一致了，那么跟随者就会拒绝接收新的日志项，并返回失败信息给领导者。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;ub0361ccd\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;uc835183c\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc835183c\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uba3e7ef9\&quot;" id="\&quot;uba3e7ef9\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">这时，领导者会递减要复制的日志项的索引值，并发送新的日志项到跟随者，这个消息的 PrevLogEntry 值为 6，PrevLogTerm 值为 3。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;ub0361ccd\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ua571d252\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua571d252\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u48cccfbb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u48cccfbb\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">如果跟随者在它的日志中，找到了 PrevLogEntry 值为 6、PrevLogTerm 值为 3 的日志项，那么日志复制 RPC 返回成功，这样一来，领导者就知道在 PrevLogEntry 值为 6、PrevLogTerm 值为 3 的位置，跟随者的日志项与自己相同。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;ub0361ccd\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u56db7787\&quot;" id="\&quot;u56db7787\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0198740b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0198740b\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">领导者通过日志复制 RPC，复制并更新覆盖该索引值之后的日志项（也就是不一致的日志项），最终实现了集群各节点日志的一致。</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua106c4f0\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua106c4f0\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u726ea4a0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u726ea4a0\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">从上面步骤中可以看到，领导者通过日志复制 RPC 一致性检查，找到跟随者节点上与自己相同日志项的最大索引值，然后复制并更新覆盖该索引值之后的日志项，实现了各节点日志的一致。需要注意的是，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf2e36d87\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf2e36d87\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">跟随者中的不一致日志项会被领导者的日志覆盖，而且领导者从来不会覆盖或者删除自己的日志</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u13ed920d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u13ed920d\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ud7f23b5d\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud7f23b5d\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u02f4802e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u02f4802e\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u53daebab\&quot;" id="\&quot;u53daebab\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2e1d41fb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2e1d41fb\&quot;">思考：</span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8de307cb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8de307cb\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">领导者接收到大多数的“复制成功”响应后，就会将日志应用到它自己的状态机，然后返回“成功”响应客户端。如果此时有个节点不在“大多数”中，也就是说它接收日志项失败，那么在这种情况下，Raft 会如何处理实现日志的一致？</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u523c6a9f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u523c6a9f\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufd0c314b\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufd0c314b\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">答案：</span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub46e2bb2\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub46e2bb2\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">这种情况下，Raft 会</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u550fcea9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u550fcea9\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">通过日志复制 RPC 的一致性检查</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u83bcab97\&quot;" id="\&quot;u83bcab97\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">，找到失败者节点上，与自己相同日志项的最大索引值，然后</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ueda0569f\&quot;" id="\&quot;ueda0569f\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">领导者强制该失败者更新覆盖的不一致日志项</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua5bbaf20\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua5bbaf20\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">，实现日志的一致。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ud42fe7c5\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud42fe7c5\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <blockquote data-lake-id="\&quot;uf6272868\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf6272868\&quot;">
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u5dcc972f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5dcc972f\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u758cffb8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u758cffb8\&quot;">参考文章：</span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;bookmarkInline\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22mode%22%3A%22title%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2F100046101%2F205784%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2F100046101%2F205784%2F%22%2C%22detail%22%3A%7B%22icon%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2Ffavicon.ico%22%2C%22image%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic001.geekbang.org%2Fresource%2Fimage%2Fd1%2Fc1%2Fd1bb8c5949d6bfe3bfd4e839e795c3c1.jpg%22%2C%22title%22%3A%2208%20%7C%20Raft%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%EF%BC%9F%22%2C%22belong%22%3A%22%E6%9E%81%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%B7%B2%E5%AE%8C%E7%BB%93%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E9%99%90%E6%97%B6%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB%22%2C%22belong_url%22%3Anull%2C%22desc%22%3A%22%E8%B7%9F%E9%9A%8F%E8%80%85%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E9%A1%B9%E4%BC%9A%E8%A2%AB%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E8%A6%86%E7%9B%96%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%94%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E8%80%85%E4%BB%8E%E6%9D%A5%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E8%A6%86%E7%9B%96%E6%88%96%E8%80%85%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E3%80%82%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2F100046101%2F205784%22%2C%22extra%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22_serializer%22%3A%22web.editor_link_detail%22%7D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22VuBR7%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  </blockquote>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u3f97ac30\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3f97ac30\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;QbThN\&quot;" id="\&quot;QbThN\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua19febcd\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua19febcd\&quot;">成员变更</span></h4>
  <h5 data-lake-id="\&quot;Gzb2T\&quot;" id="\&quot;Gzb2T\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue45f0445\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue45f0445\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(36,="" 41,="" 46)\"="">配置说明</span></h5>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u4e5e3770\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4e5e3770\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue16b9188\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue16b9188\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(36,="" 41,="" 46)\"="">在分布式系统中，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;udd5f3757\&quot;" id="\&quot;udd5f3757\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(36,="" 41,="" 46)\"="">成员变更（即动态调整集群中的节点集合）</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u09d1652a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u09d1652a\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(36,="" 41,="" 46)\"="">是一个重要的需求。Raft 算法采用了一种安全且高效的方法来处理这个问题，称为</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue9b5f5ff\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue9b5f5ff\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(36,="" 41,="" 46)\"="">“联合共识”机制（Joint Consensus）</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua957b003\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua957b003\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(36,="" 41,="" 46)\"="">。这个机制确保在进行成员变更时不会影响集群的可用性和一致性。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u87d1bfb5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u87d1bfb5\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud6e6b7da\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud6e6b7da\&quot;">在介绍节点变更过程之间，需要先明确一个概念：</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u085f16b7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u085f16b7\&quot;">配置（configuration）。</span></strong></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u2c02356d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2c02356d\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf732eb5b\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf732eb5b\&quot;">在raft算法中，使用用配置（configuration）来表示集群的节点集合，比如某个集群由A、B、C三个节点构成，那么集群的配置就是[A，B，C]，在稳定的状态下，所有节点的配置都相同。从这里就可以知道，每个节点是通过这个配置信息来获取集群状态的，比如在选举，日志同步过程中，集群中有哪几个Follower，Leader需要向哪几个节点发送 RPC 通信都需要通过配置（configuration）来获取。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ud87883fd\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud87883fd\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h5 data-lake-id="\&quot;XPBY9\&quot;" id="\&quot;XPBY9\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ubf443c24\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubf443c24\&quot;">存在问题</span></h5>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u9098ba87\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9098ba87\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u78a318bc\&quot;" id="\&quot;u78a318bc\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">在集群中进行成员变更的最大风险是，可能会</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uff76c304\&quot;" id="\&quot;uff76c304\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">同时出现 2 个领导者</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9e234017\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9e234017\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ud74ec247\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud74ec247\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2b060737\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2b060737\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">比如在进行成员变更时，节点 A、B 和 C 之间发生了分区错误，节点 A、B 组成旧配置中的“大多数”，也就是变更前的 3 节点集群中的“大多数”，那么这时的领导者（节点 A）依旧是领导者。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u86fab4b7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u86fab4b7\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4fdde3d2\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4fdde3d2\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">另一方面，节点 C 和新节点 D、E 组成了新配置的“大多数”，也就是变更后的 5 节点集群中的“大多数”，它们可能会选举出新的领导者（比如节点 C）。那么这时，就出现了同时存在 2 个领导者的情况。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ubf947fda\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubf947fda\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733584518979-dd380b79-2052-4050-ab85-18ffb61183fb.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uc65f44fd-f936-4fe0-acce-fc6e86e1a6f%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u557dc0ce-6321-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A694.5%2C%22height%22%3A178%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A105067%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A681%2C%22originHeight%22%3A175%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%96%B0%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B0%2C3%E4%B8%AA%22%2C%22x%22%3A321%2C%22y%22%3A136%2C%22width%22%3A166%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%97%A7%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B02%E4%B8%AA%22%2C%22x%22%3A23%2C%22y%22%3A137%2C%22width%22%3A171%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221%22%2C%22x%22%3A284%2C%22y%22%3A21%2C%22width%22%3A13%2C%22height%22%3A131%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221%22%2C%22x%22%3A306%2C%22y%22%3A34%2C%22width%22%3A11%2C%22height%22%3A113%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A115%2C%22y%22%3A31%2C%22width%22%3A53%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A217%2C%22y%22%3A86%2C%22width%22%3A51%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9D%22%2C%22x%22%3A434%2C%22y%22%3A86%2C%22width%22%3A49%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A336%2C%22y%22%3A86%2C%22width%22%3A49%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A335%2C%22y%22%3A31%2C%22width%22%3A51%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9E%22%2C%22x%22%3A529%2C%22y%22%3A86%2C%22width%22%3A54%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A118%2C%22y%22%3A86%2C%22width%22%3A50%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%87%8D%E4%BD%9C%E4%BD%9C%E4%BD%9C%E4%BD%9C%E8%BD%A6%22%2C%22x%22%3A347%2C%22y%22%3A157%2C%22width%22%3A112%2C%22height%22%3A8%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%22%2C%22x%22%3A656%2C%22y%22%3A45%2C%22width%22%3A13%2C%22height%22%3A111%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fcfcfa%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u8cc5cb51%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u4ec7dc1a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4ec7dc1a\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u51f10b13\&quot;" id="\&quot;u51f10b13\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">当出现了 2 个领导者，就违背了“领导者的唯一性”的原则，进而影响到集群的稳定运行。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u3f9a71b9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3f9a71b9\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h5 data-lake-id="\&quot;n82eM\&quot;" id="\&quot;n82eM\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufd7a37e0\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufd7a37e0\&quot;">变更策略</span></h5>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u78bbddb4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u78bbddb4\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u36012d7b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u36012d7b\&quot;">变更策略主要有以下两种：</span></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;u81662958\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u7b454db9\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u1d36f6f7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1d36f6f7\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uaef3fb86\&quot;" id="\&quot;uaef3fb86\&quot;">串行变更</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;u7b454db9\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ufe35e9a1\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufe35e9a1\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufcb06a9a\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufcb06a9a\&quot;">单节点变更</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uc5259730\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc5259730\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u02641e37\&quot;" id="\&quot;u02641e37\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;udf243e97\&quot;" id="\&quot;udf243e97\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9610332a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9610332a\&quot;">详细说明：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u498104d2\&quot;" id="\&quot;u498104d2\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u858eabc0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u858eabc0\&quot;">串行变更</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud31c535a\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud31c535a\&quot;">：这种方法就是先将集群原来所有节点关闭，更新其配置后，再启动新的集群，显然这种方法很安全，可以保证集群始终只有一个Leader，但是这种方法会导致每次成员变更时都需要关闭集群，导致集群无法对外提供服务，对于高可用的业务场景显然不适用。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u809183c6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u809183c6\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u7bd8f6a7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7bd8f6a7\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u33f45dec\&quot;" id="\&quot;u33f45dec\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">单节点变更</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uaae0d8fd\&quot;" id="\&quot;uaae0d8fd\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">（常用）：就是通过</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7a33bfee\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7a33bfee\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">一次变更一个节点</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf8475241\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf8475241\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">实现成员变更。</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u77572c7d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u77572c7d\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">如果需要变更多个节点，那你需要执行多次单节点变更</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7c3de0e3\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7c3de0e3\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">。比如将 3 节点集群扩容为 5 节点集群，这时需要执行 2 次单节点变更，先将 3 节点集群变更为 4 节点集群，然后再将 4 节点集群变更为 5 节点集群。如下图：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ue1dfdab0\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue1dfdab0\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733585118255-c669c0d2-b38b-426a-a76a-6a18f93e38fa.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u46768b0a-1784-4fc6-b14f-04be71ee557%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u557dc0ce-6321-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A574.5%2C%22height%22%3A393%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A228984%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A669%2C%22originHeight%22%3A458%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%222.%E5%B0%864%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E5%8F%98%E6%9B%B4%E4%B8%BA5%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%22%2C%22x%22%3A35%2C%22y%22%3A242%2C%22width%22%3A287%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221.%E5%B0%863%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E5%8F%98%E6%9B%B4%E4%B8%BA4%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%22%2C%22x%22%3A36%2C%22y%22%3A16%2C%22width%22%3A287%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22RAF%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%22%2C%22x%22%3A47%2C%22y%22%3A282%2C%22width%22%3A84%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22RAF%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%22%2C%22x%22%3A49%2C%22y%22%3A62%2C%22width%22%3A88%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A60%2C%22y%22%3A350%2C%22width%22%3A64%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A300%2C%22y%22%3A350%2C%22width%22%3A58%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9D%22%2C%22x%22%3A418%2C%22y%22%3A350%2C%22width%22%3A58%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A182%2C%22y%22%3A135%2C%22width%22%3A61%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A301%2C%22y%22%3A135%2C%22width%22%3A62%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A62%2C%22y%22%3A136%2C%22width%22%3A63%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221%22%2C%22x%22%3A27%2C%22y%22%3A61%2C%22width%22%3A11%2C%22height%22%3A146%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A181%2C%22y%22%3A350%2C%22width%22%3A58%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221%22%2C%22x%22%3A625%2C%22y%22%3A283%2C%22width%22%3A14%2C%22height%22%3A152%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%227%22%2C%22x%22%3A24%2C%22y%22%3A287%2C%22width%22%3A11%2C%22height%22%3A93%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%8D%81%22%2C%22x%22%3A434%2C%22y%22%3A130%2C%22width%22%3A35%2C%22height%22%3A39%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221%22%2C%22x%22%3A24%2C%22y%22%3A309%2C%22width%22%3A11%2C%22height%22%3A92%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fdfdfb%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ueb649987%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u9bb5731b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9bb5731b\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;udae794a3\&quot;" id="\&quot;udae794a3\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1aa2f101\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1aa2f101\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">现在，回到刚开始的问题，看看如何用单节点变更的方法，解决这个问题。为了演示方便，假设节点 A 是领导者：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u9ef31588\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9ef31588\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733585273647-eb5f7f42-6983-45c3-8312-1409e6f4d5ca.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uab07f3f3-f7b5-4133-a7d8-dfd1f37ce33%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u557dc0ce-6321-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A395%2C%22height%22%3A227%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A155691%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A626%2C%22originHeight%22%3A360%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22RAF%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%22%2C%22x%22%3A241%2C%22y%22%3A30%2C%22width%22%3A134%2C%22height%22%3A35%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A65%2C%22y%22%3A92%2C%22width%22%3A101%2C%22height%22%3A38%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A67%2C%22y%22%3A202%2C%22width%22%3A103%2C%22height%22%3A39%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A261%2C%22y%22%3A202%2C%22width%22%3A98%2C%22height%22%3A40%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A455%2C%22y%22%3A202%2C%22width%22%3A97%2C%22height%22%3A41%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%2217%22%2C%22x%22%3A9%2C%22y%22%3A73%2C%22width%22%3A11%2C%22height%22%3A235%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fdfdfb%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u444d287a%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u9e6cb00d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9e6cb00d\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5e09e2ac\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5e09e2ac\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">目前的集群配置为 [A, B, C]，我们先向集群中加入节点 D，这意味着新配置为 [A, B, C, D]。成员变更，是通过这么两步实现的：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ued3a0666\&quot;" id="\&quot;ued3a0666\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733585332865-c9aaebf7-d4b4-450d-a0da-b6d3146ef4c5.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ua7e63053-cb19-4133-825b-f50c527c0d0%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u557dc0ce-6321-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A477%2C%22height%22%3A217%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A124265%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A614%2C%22originHeight%22%3A279%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A52%2C%22y%22%3A154%2C%22width%22%3A78%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22RAF%E4%B8%AA%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%22%2C%22x%22%3A259%2C%22y%22%3A31%2C%22width%22%3A98%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9D%22%2C%22x%22%3A482%2C%22y%22%3A154%2C%22width%22%3A76%2C%22height%22%3A33%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A197%2C%22y%22%3A155%2C%22width%22%3A72%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A341%2C%22y%22%3A155%2C%22width%22%3A72%2C%22height%22%3A32%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A52%2C%22y%22%3A73%2C%22width%22%3A75%2C%22height%22%3A29%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221%22%2C%22x%22%3A8%2C%22y%22%3A60%2C%22width%22%3A9%2C%22height%22%3A174%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%22%2C%22x%22%3A8%2C%22y%22%3A28%2C%22width%22%3A9%2C%22height%22%3A100%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fdfdfb%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ua3f3b82b%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;u1825008c\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;ube1f2425\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ud8db11e4\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud8db11e4\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub68ec89e\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub68ec89e\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">第一步，领导者（节点 A）向新节点（节点 D）同步数据。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;ube1f2425\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ud5150cb3\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud5150cb3\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u45d28999\&quot;" id="\&quot;u45d28999\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">第二步，领导者（节点 A）将新配置[A, B, C, D]作为一个日志项，复制到新配置中所有节点（节点 A、B、C、D）上，然后将新配置的日志项应用（Apply）到本地状态机，完成单节点变更。</span></li>
  </ul>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u5661ec99\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5661ec99\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ube449e23\&quot;" id="\&quot;ube449e23\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5d8ef9dc\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5d8ef9dc\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">在变更完成后，现在的集群配置就是[A, B, C, D]，我们再向集群中加入节点 E，也就是说，新配置为[A, B, C, D, E]。成员变更的步骤和上面类似：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u2038fa3b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2038fa3b\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733585468556-662f676c-1386-4236-bf1a-42e60dfe1f98.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u46322ac7-c18c-4452-a82b-5ccbc6588dd%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u557dc0ce-6321-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A479%2C%22height%22%3A175%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A109413%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A636%2C%22originHeight%22%3A232%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22RAF%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%22%2C%22x%22%3A274%2C%22y%22%3A25%2C%22width%22%3A81%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A44%2C%22y%22%3A129%2C%22width%22%3A63%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A164%2C%22y%22%3A129%2C%22width%22%3A60%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%227%22%2C%22x%22%3A5%2C%22y%22%3A52%2C%22width%22%3A12%2C%22height%22%3A146%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A521%2C%22y%22%3A129%2C%22width%22%3A60%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9D%22%2C%22x%22%3A402%2C%22y%22%3A129%2C%22width%22%3A59%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A284%2C%22y%22%3A129%2C%22width%22%3A59%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E8%80%85%22%2C%22x%22%3A42%2C%22y%22%3A62%2C%22width%22%3A63%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221%22%2C%22x%22%3A614%2C%22y%22%3A74%2C%22width%22%3A12%2C%22height%22%3A127%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fdfdfb%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ua06a5528%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;u18ea4628\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;ud760e215\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u4c79e3ae\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4c79e3ae\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u69d9995c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u69d9995c\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">第一步，领导者（节点 A）向新节点（节点 E）同步数据。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;ud760e215\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u7994504d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7994504d\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u59ab1347\&quot;" id="\&quot;u59ab1347\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">第二步，领导者（节点 A）将新配置[A, B, C, D, E]作为一个日志项，复制到新配置中的所有节点（A、B、C、D、E）上，然后再将新配置的日志项应用到本地状态机，完成单节点变更。</span></li>
  </ul>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uf581a12a\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf581a12a\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uefc6ea82\&quot;" id="\&quot;uefc6ea82\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">这样一来，就通过一次变更一个节点的方式，完成了成员变更，保证了集群中始终只有一个领导者，而且集群也在稳定运行，持续提供服务。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u0c92ed3d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0c92ed3d\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ud321d646\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud321d646\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua4654c1e\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua4654c1e\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">在正常情况下，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufdf7e700\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufdf7e700\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0)\"="">不管旧的集群配置是怎么组成的，旧配置的“大多数”和新配置的“大多数”都会有至少一个节点是重叠的。</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua4952dbb\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua4952dbb\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"=""> 也就是说，不会同时存在旧配置和新配置 2 个“大多数”：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ue939a79a\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue939a79a\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733585636719-d0f24a81-8233-4c16-bfe3-447f0cb30355.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u8e46512a-5e8f-4982-90c9-3c74feb9227%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u557dc0ce-6321-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A468%2C%22height%22%3A787%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A410226%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A526%2C%22originHeight%22%3A885%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22.%E4%BB%8E5%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%BB%E9%99%A41%E4%B8%AA%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A17%2C%22y%22%3A854%2C%22width%22%3A241%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%97%A5%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B0%2C2%E4%B8%AA%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%3A%22%2C%22x%22%3A62%2C%22y%22%3A20%2C%22width%22%3A213%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%222.%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A01%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B0%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E5%88%B04%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%22%2C%22x%22%3A16%2C%22y%22%3A392%2C%22width%22%3A242%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22.%E4%BB%8E4%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%BB%E9%99%A41%E4%B8%AA%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A17%2C%22y%22%3A629%2C%22width%22%3A242%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%97%A7%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B0%2C3%E4%B8%AA%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A14%2C%22y%22%3A474%2C%22width%22%3A203%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%96%B0%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B0%2C3%E4%B8%AA%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A309%2C%22y%22%3A354%2C%22width%22%3A204%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%97%A7%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B0%2C3%E4%B8%AA%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A18%2C%22y%22%3A235%2C%22width%22%3A193%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%96%B0%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B0%2C3%E4%B8%AA%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A303%2C%22y%22%3A808%2C%22width%22%3A207%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221.%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A01%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B0%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E5%88%B03%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%22%2C%22x%22%3A24%2C%22y%22%3A183%2C%22width%22%3A246%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%97%A7%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B0%2C3%E4%B8%AA%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A17%2C%22y%22%3A692%2C%22width%22%3A198%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%96%B0%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B0%2C3%E4%B8%AA%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A284%2C%22y%22%3A139%2C%22width%22%3A202%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%96%B0%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B0%2C2%E4%B8%AA%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%3A%22%2C%22x%22%3A307%2C%22y%22%3A593%2C%22width%22%3A212%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221%22%2C%22x%22%3A9%2C%22y%22%3A258%2C%22width%22%3A14%2C%22height%22%3A103%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%8F%B7%22%2C%22x%22%3A124%2C%22y%22%3A61%2C%22width%22%3A18%2C%22height%22%3A54%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AE%89%22%2C%22x%22%3A72%2C%22y%22%3A282%2C%22width%22%3A20%2C%22height%22%3A56%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%22%2C%22x%22%3A83%2C%22y%22%3A40%2C%22width%22%3A185%2C%22height%22%3A14%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%2211%22%2C%22x%22%3A129%2C%22y%22%3A711%2C%22width%22%3A124%2C%22height%22%3A12%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%224%22%2C%22x%22%3A69%2C%22y%22%3A7%2C%22width%22%3A194%2C%22height%22%3A11%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%22%2C%22x%22%3A159%2C%22y%22%3A280%2C%22width%22%3A14%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%22%2C%22x%22%3A297%2C%22y%22%3A66%2C%22width%22%3A20%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A206%2C%22y%22%3A97%2C%22width%22%3A26%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%22%2C%22x%22%3A154%2C%22y%22%3A736%2C%22width%22%3A24%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%22%2C%22x%22%3A209%2C%22y%22%3A66%2C%22width%22%3A22%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A156%2C%22y%22%3A543%2C%22width%22%3A20%2C%22height%22%3A33%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%22%2C%22x%22%3A157%2C%22y%22%3A519%2C%22width%22%3A18%2C%22height%22%3A32%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%BD%A6%22%2C%22x%22%3A170%2C%22y%22%3A56%2C%22width%22%3A14%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A298%2C%22y%22%3A90%2C%22width%22%3A18%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%3A%22%2C%22x%22%3A206%2C%22y%22%3A275%2C%22width%22%3A9%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%87%8D%E5%9B%BD%E5%9B%BD%E5%9B%BD%E7%94%9F%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E4%BA%A7%E4%BA%A7%E4%BA%A7%22%2C%22x%22%3A292%2C%22y%22%3A161%2C%22width%22%3A156%2C%22height%22%3A10%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%82%B9%22%2C%22x%22%3A154%2C%22y%22%3A770%2C%22width%22%3A25%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f8d0b1%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u1536b235%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ue51f28f4\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue51f28f4\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5c37eb15\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5c37eb15\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">从上图可以看出，不管原集群节点数是奇数还是偶数，也不管是在原集群上新增一个节点还是删除一个节点，在集群的节点数变更之后，原集群的多数派和新集群的多数派</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2aff13d1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2aff13d1\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">一定存在交集</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc0e243c2\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc0e243c2\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">，那么再同一个任期内，原集群C_old和新集群C_new中交集的那一个节点只会进行一次投票，要么投票给C_old，要么投票给C_new，这样就避免可同一任期出现在两个Leader的现象。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u2d859c83\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2d859c83\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u32fd3626\&quot;" id="\&quot;u32fd3626\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub21d34f2\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub21d34f2\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">需要注意的是，在分区错误、节点故障等情况下，如果我们并发执行单节点变更，那么就可能出现一次单节点变更尚未完成，新的单节点变更又在执行，导致集群出现 2 个领导者的情况。</span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u661d9a12\&quot;" id="\&quot;u661d9a12\&quot;"><br /></span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;udd3ab106\&quot;" id="\&quot;udd3ab106\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">如果遇到这种情况，可以在领导者启动时，创建一个 NO_OP 日志项（也就是空日志项），只有当领导者将 NO_OP 日志项应用后，再执行成员变更请求。具体的实现，可参考 Hashicorp Raft 的源码，也就是 runLeader() 函数中：</span></p>
  <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;codeblock\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22c%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22noop%20%3A%3D%20%26logFuture%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20log%3A%20Log%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20Type%3A%20LogNoop%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D%2C%5Cn%7D%5Cnr.dispatchLogs(%5B%5D*logFuture%7Bnoop%7D)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22default%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22usOAI%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u4f73f861\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4f73f861\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <blockquote data-lake-id="\&quot;u3f9d93f1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3f9d93f1\&quot;">
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u0e8fc326\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0e8fc326\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u686f2b63\&quot;" id="\&quot;u686f2b63\&quot;">参考文章：</span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;bookmarkInline\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22mode%22%3A%22title%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2F100046101%2F206274%2F%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2F100046101%2F206274%2F%22%2C%22detail%22%3A%7B%22icon%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2Ffavicon.ico%22%2C%22image%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic001.geekbang.org%2Fresource%2Fimage%2F2c%2Ff8%2F2caafbb13420ef0766ecd9150fcad5f8.jpg%22%2C%22title%22%3A%2209%20%7C%20Raft%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%88%90%E5%91%98%E5%8F%98%E6%9B%B4%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%9F%22%2C%22belong%22%3A%22%E6%9E%81%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%B7%B2%E5%AE%8C%E7%BB%93%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E9%99%90%E6%97%B6%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB%22%2C%22belong_url%22%3Anull%2C%22desc%22%3A%22%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E5%85%B1%E8%AF%86%E4%B8%8D%E5%A5%BD%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%9D%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B0Raft%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%EF%BC%8C%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%8D%95%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E5%8F%98%E6%9B%B4%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%88%E6%AF%94%E5%A6%82Etcd%E3%80%81Hashicorp%20Raft%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2F100046101%2F206274%2F%22%2C%22extra%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22_serializer%22%3A%22web.editor_link_detail%22%7D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Pic1G%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  </blockquote>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u5d40de33\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5d40de33\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h3 data-lake-id="\&quot;MP8mo\&quot;" id="\&quot;MP8mo\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u226f8730\&quot;" id="\&quot;u226f8730\&quot;">一致性哈希</span></h3>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;WiEdq\&quot;" id="\&quot;WiEdq\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u19a5205f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u19a5205f\&quot;">哈希问题</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u28ee7d69\&quot;" id="\&quot;u28ee7d69\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2b7f076c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2b7f076c\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">如果通过 Raft 算法实现了 KV 存储，虽然领导者模型简化了算法实现和共识协商，但</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;udc7256f9\&quot;" id="\&quot;udc7256f9\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">写请求只能限制在领导者节点上处理</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8e2c4eb2\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8e2c4eb2\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">，导致了集群的接入性能约等于单机，那么随着业务发展，集群的性能可能就扛不住了，会造成系统过载和服务不可用。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ubfea2936\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubfea2936\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub15c51dd\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub15c51dd\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">这时就要通过分集群，突破单集群的性能限制了。可以加个 Proxy 层（参考 Codis Redis 架构），由 Proxy 层处理来自客户端的读写请求，接收到读写请求后，通过对 Key 做哈希找到对应的集群就可以了。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u93e05baf\&quot;" id="\&quot;u93e05baf\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u75b52bc9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u75b52bc9\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u030a7635\&quot;" id="\&quot;u030a7635\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">但有个明显的缺点：当需要变更集群数时（比如从 2 个集群扩展为 3 个集群），这时大部分的数据都需要迁移，重新映射，数据的迁移成本是非常高的。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u20495fb2\&quot;" id="\&quot;u20495fb2\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u17edd12c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u17edd12c\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uede2def6\&quot;" id="\&quot;uede2def6\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u61b91b70\&quot;" id="\&quot;u61b91b70\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">场景演示：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ucf830549\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucf830549\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5288b42e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5288b42e\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">假设有一个由 A、B、C 三个节点组成（为了方便演示，使用节点来替代集群）的 KV 服务，每个节点存放不同的 KV 数据：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua0bd33ee\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua0bd33ee\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733637749140-8dd24b2a-0b3f-4fc1-9746-cdeb38fbc937.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u6900a659-9521-411e-bb8f-11f475549c6%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u557dc0ce-6321-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A494%2C%22height%22%3A385%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A195821%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A642%2C%22originHeight%22%3A500%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A489%2C%22y%22%3A402%2C%22width%22%3A82%2C%22height%22%3A35%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A278%2C%22y%22%3A415%2C%22width%22%3A81%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E7%AB%AF%22%2C%22x%22%3A266%2C%22y%22%3A55%2C%22width%22%3A101%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A65%2C%22y%22%3A410%2C%22width%22%3A84%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22PROXU%22%2C%22x%22%3A273%2C%22y%22%3A222%2C%22width%22%3A86%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fdfdfb%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ue1714273%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ud8616d88\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud8616d88\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8fd6caa7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8fd6caa7\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">通过哈希算法，每个 key 都可以寻址到对应的服务器，比如，查询 key 是 key-01，计算公式为 hash(key-01) % 3 ，经过计算寻址到了编号为 1 的服务器节点 A。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u57ff8f8e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u57ff8f8e\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733637778316-93ec983c-8bb1-4836-bd0c-167cdb738a88.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u137ce606-9de4-4fa8-99f9-f87f1777b2f%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u557dc0ce-6321-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A497.5%2C%22height%22%3A398%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A195747%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A595%2C%22originHeight%22%3A476%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22HASH(KEY-O7)%22%2C%22x%22%3A17%2C%22y%22%3A271%2C%22width%22%3A150%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E7%AB%AF%22%2C%22x%22%3A260%2C%22y%22%3A48%2C%22width%22%3A99%2C%22height%22%3A35%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A63%2C%22y%22%3A398%2C%22width%22%3A79%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A272%2C%22y%22%3A402%2C%22width%22%3A79%2C%22height%22%3A32%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A478%2C%22y%22%3A390%2C%22width%22%3A81%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22PROXU%22%2C%22x%22%3A265%2C%22y%22%3A214%2C%22width%22%3A86%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%253%3D1%22%2C%22x%22%3A178%2C%22y%22%3A271%2C%22width%22%3A64%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fcfcfa%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u12730dc7%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ueb314a7a\&quot;" id="\&quot;ueb314a7a\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud0bdaed9\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud0bdaed9\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">但如果服务器数量发生变化，基于新的服务器数量来执行哈希算法的时候，就会出现路由寻址失败的情况，Proxy 无法找到之前寻址到的那个服务器节点。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u06f7d67d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u06f7d67d\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf07c774f\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf07c774f\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">想象一下，假如 3 个节点不能满足业务需要了，这时增加了一个节点，节点的数量从 3 变化为 4，那么之前的 hash(key-01) % 3 = 1，就变成了 hash(key-01) % 4 = X，因为取模运算发生了变化，所以这个 X 大概率不是 1（可能 X 为 2），这时你再查询，就会找不到数据了，因为 key-01 对应的数据，存储在节点 A 上，而不是节点 B：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u581e8a6b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u581e8a6b\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733637824210-84eea829-0b67-4a01-948c-cc5806d6e853.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uf68efb6e-6ecf-41a9-865f-d27f74c2b87%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u557dc0ce-6321-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A497%2C%22height%22%3A314%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A170826%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A640%2C%22originHeight%22%3A404%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22HASH(KEY-0T%254%3D2%22%2C%22x%22%3A166%2C%22y%22%3A237%2C%22width%22%3A166%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E7%AB%AF%22%2C%22x%22%3A248%2C%22y%22%3A37%2C%22width%22%3A72%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A48%2C%22y%22%3A287%2C%22width%22%3A63%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9D%22%2C%22x%22%3A533%2C%22y%22%3A299%2C%22width%22%3A59%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A230%2C%22y%22%3A329%2C%22width%22%3A57%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A409%2C%22y%22%3A303%2C%22width%22%3A59%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22PROXU%22%2C%22x%22%3A252%2C%22y%22%3A158%2C%22width%22%3A64%2C%22height%22%3A17%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fbfbfb%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u86faa540%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uaf32a2f9\&quot;" id="\&quot;uaf32a2f9\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5ec9247f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5ec9247f\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">同样的道理，如果需要下线 1 个服务器节点（也就是缩容），也会存在类似的可能查询不到数据的问题。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u71269b7f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u71269b7f\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud57ac3c0\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud57ac3c0\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">而解决这个问题的办法，在于迁移数据，基于新的计算公式 hash(key-01) % 4 ，来重新对数据和节点做映射。需要注意的是，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u554cc285\&quot;" id="\&quot;u554cc285\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">数据的迁移成本是非常高的</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue5b1a080\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue5b1a080\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u695ca545\&quot;" id="\&quot;u695ca545\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub3190887\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub3190887\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u3d55648b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3d55648b\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucac62e3f\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucac62e3f\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">举个例子，对于 1000 万 key 的 3 节点 KV 存储，如果增加 1 个节点，变为 4 节点集群，则需要迁移 75% 的数据。</span></p>
  <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;codeblock\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22go%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%24%20go%20run%20.%2Fhash.go%20%20-keys%2010000000%20-nodes%203%20-new-nodes%204%5Cn74.999980%25%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22default%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22gFSID%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u9a9a8415\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9a9a8415\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;ILeNu\&quot;" id="\&quot;ILeNu\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6712d6d9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6712d6d9\&quot;">一致哈希</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ucaee2922\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucaee2922\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uff9f790f\&quot;" id="\&quot;uff9f790f\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(36,="" 41,="" 46)\"="">一致性哈希（Consistent Hashing）</span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u48b3b315\&quot;" id="\&quot;u48b3b315\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">也用了取模运算，但与哈希算法不同的是，哈希算法是对节点的数量进行取模运算，而</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0b16b7cc\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0b16b7cc\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">一致哈希算法是对 2^32 进行取模运算</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u09636738\&quot;" id="\&quot;u09636738\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u065dc158\&quot;" id="\&quot;u065dc158\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5b6a6c91\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5b6a6c91\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">一致哈希算法就是将整个哈希值空间组织成一个</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u198103cd\&quot;" id="\&quot;u198103cd\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">虚拟的圆环</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucaaceeac\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucaaceeac\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">，也就是</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u255740a8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u255740a8\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">哈希环</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0e92d9f1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0e92d9f1\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u136239e7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u136239e7\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733652911416-70ad613b-d838-4736-863b-412bceab1683.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22udb85a5fc-50fe-4008-a933-404dd0f3049%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u557dc0ce-6321-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A417.5%2C%22height%22%3A465%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A143943%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A589%2C%22originHeight%22%3A656%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fcfdfd%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ua44b16d6%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;udccfedf4\&quot;" id="\&quot;udccfedf4\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc7837672\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc7837672\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">可以看到，哈希环的空间是按顺时针方向组织的，圆环的正上方的点代表 0，0 点右侧的第一个点代表 1，以此类推，2、3、4、5、6……直到 2^32-1，也就是说 0 点左侧的第一个点代表 2^32-1。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua4ebfd11\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua4ebfd11\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u28186519\&quot;" id="\&quot;u28186519\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uef6109ac\&quot;" id="\&quot;uef6109ac\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u47b6f1b8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u47b6f1b8\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">在一致哈希中，可以通过执行哈希算法（为了演示方便，假设哈希算法函数为“</span><code data-lake-id="\&quot;u1a8e656e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1a8e656e\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8e292658\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8e292658\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">c-hash()</span></code><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4d055d44\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4d055d44\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">”），将节点映射到哈希环上，比如选择节点的主机名作为参数执行 </span><code data-lake-id="\&quot;u0e895a54\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0e895a54\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub4d93c85\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub4d93c85\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">c-hash()</span></code><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u454d50ca\&quot;" id="\&quot;u454d50ca\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">，那么每个节点就能确定其在哈希环上的位置了：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua37ae731\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua37ae731\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733653027210-f268f758-9951-465e-a93b-ef1a871376b8.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u7ee0860f-8dc3-408d-94f6-effb196ff4e%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u557dc0ce-6321-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A429%2C%22height%22%3A434%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A176735%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A614%2C%22originHeight%22%3A621%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22232-110%22%2C%22x%22%3A187%2C%22y%22%3A10%2C%22width%22%3A152%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A274%2C%22y%22%3A549%2C%22width%22%3A81%2C%22height%22%3A33%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A28%2C%22y%22%3A315%2C%22width%22%3A80%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A499%2C%22y%22%3A260%2C%22width%22%3A89%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fcfdfd%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u92a7de46%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ud6ed48c0\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud6ed48c0\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub4d0275a\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub4d0275a\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">当需要对指定 key 的值进行读写的时候，可以通过下面 2 步进行寻址：</span></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;u1bce0cf0\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u125863b2\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u252df9c2\&quot;" id="\&quot;u252df9c2\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u82307ca8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u82307ca8\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">将 key 作为参数执行 </span><code data-lake-id="\&quot;ub0f3de83\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub0f3de83\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub6b8b92d\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub6b8b92d\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">c-hash()</span></code><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u39d63676\&quot;" id="\&quot;u39d63676\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"=""> 计算哈希值，并确定此 key 在环上的位置。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;u125863b2\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u8c8783b4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8c8783b4\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5839d882\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5839d882\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">从这个位置沿着哈希环</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u96cd86f7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u96cd86f7\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">顺时针“行走”</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue7f32586\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue7f32586\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">，遇到的第一节点就是 key 对应的节点。</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ub58a661e\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub58a661e\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u300969df\&quot;" id="\&quot;u300969df\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u4f6352fb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4f6352fb\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua21162ec\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua21162ec\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">举个例子，假设 key-01、key-02、key-03 三个 key，经过哈希算法 </span><code data-lake-id="\&quot;ue27d7534\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue27d7534\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6698f385\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6698f385\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">c-hash()</span></code><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9b8b7d11\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9b8b7d11\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"=""> 计算后，在哈希环上的位置如下图：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u60a78013\&quot;" id="\&quot;u60a78013\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733653129455-78218906-16ec-481c-add5-838685f2f869.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ud27e6926-e080-4dad-adf0-4ac3125b340%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u557dc0ce-6321-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A443.5%2C%22height%22%3A416%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A182146%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A603%2C%22originHeight%22%3A565%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22KEY-03%22%2C%22x%22%3A21%2C%22y%22%3A439%2C%22width%22%3A85%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A262%2C%22y%22%3A500%2C%22width%22%3A79%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A470%2C%22y%22%3A233%2C%22width%22%3A84%2C%22height%22%3A32%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22KEY-O2%22%2C%22x%22%3A486%2C%22y%22%3A438%2C%22width%22%3A87%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22232-1%22%2C%22x%22%3A187%2C%22y%22%3A7%2C%22width%22%3A91%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22KEY-01%22%2C%22x%22%3A458%2C%22y%22%3A101%2C%22width%22%3A80%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A37%2C%22y%22%3A285%2C%22width%22%3A77%2C%22height%22%3A32%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f5f6f5%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u38f9f1f9%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u904de748\&quot;" id="\&quot;u904de748\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u15e90410\&quot;" id="\&quot;u15e90410\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">那么根据一致哈希算法，key-01 将寻址到节点 A，key-02 将寻址到节点 B，key-03 将寻址到节点 C。<br /><br /></span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u837a87ae\&quot;" id="\&quot;u837a87ae\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1b6674ac\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1b6674ac\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">一致哈希是如何避免哈希算法的问题的。假设，现在有一个节点故障了（比如节点 C）：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u8a9378c0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8a9378c0\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733653205820-fe2729bc-d5cc-49f1-8437-4c32afe458ae.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u6d032a0a-5a56-4d78-9423-597ca660c5f%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u557dc0ce-6321-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A453.5%2C%22height%22%3A438%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A193252%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A599%2C%22originHeight%22%3A579%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22232-10%22%2C%22x%22%3A188%2C%22y%22%3A12%2C%22width%22%3A146%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A475%2C%22y%22%3A238%2C%22width%22%3A84%2C%22height%22%3A35%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A265%2C%22y%22%3A507%2C%22width%22%3A78%2C%22height%22%3A35%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A36%2C%22y%22%3A291%2C%22width%22%3A79%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22KEY-O7%22%2C%22x%22%3A459%2C%22y%22%3A105%2C%22width%22%3A87%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22KEY-03%22%2C%22x%22%3A20%2C%22y%22%3A445%2C%22width%22%3A86%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22KEY-O2%22%2C%22x%22%3A491%2C%22y%22%3A448%2C%22width%22%3A86%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23dbdddb%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u96756d38%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uc9711351\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc9711351\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ude7039ed\&quot;" id="\&quot;ude7039ed\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">可以看到，key-01 和 key-02 不会受到影响，只有 key-03 的寻址被</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1113f41e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1113f41e\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">重定位</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5a4d0c33\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5a4d0c33\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">到 A。一般来说，在一致哈希算法中，如果某个节点宕机不可用了，那么受影响的数据仅仅是，会寻址到此节点和前一节点之间的数据。比如当节点 C 宕机了，受影响的数据是会寻址到节点 B 和节点 C 之间的数据（例如 key-03），寻址到其他哈希环空间的数据（例如 key-01），不会受到影响。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u982bcda3\&quot;" id="\&quot;u982bcda3\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2882a086\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2882a086\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">那如果此时集群不能满足业务的需求，需要扩容一个节点（也就是增加一个节点，比如 D）：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u01533aca\&quot;" id="\&quot;u01533aca\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733653257880-26a95736-e736-4880-9101-7fc677ed1179.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u0029c48c-02f7-40d5-8be1-64d5ccab53a%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u557dc0ce-6321-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A458.5%2C%22height%22%3A449%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A198980%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A603%2C%22originHeight%22%3A591%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%2232-0%22%2C%22x%22%3A190%2C%22y%22%3A10%2C%22width%22%3A142%2C%22height%22%3A40%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9D%22%2C%22x%22%3A33%2C%22y%22%3A297%2C%22width%22%3A78%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A96%2C%22y%22%3A139%2C%22width%22%3A81%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22KEY-03%22%2C%22x%22%3A19%2C%22y%22%3A457%2C%22width%22%3A87%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22KEY-O2%22%2C%22x%22%3A497%2C%22y%22%3A456%2C%22width%22%3A89%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A485%2C%22y%22%3A243%2C%22width%22%3A82%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A269%2C%22y%22%3A519%2C%22width%22%3A77%2C%22height%22%3A33%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22KEY-07%22%2C%22x%22%3A465%2C%22y%22%3A106%2C%22width%22%3A89%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f8f9f9%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u4af4b7ab%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u684dadf5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u684dadf5\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u38cf3356\&quot;" id="\&quot;u38cf3356\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">可以看到，key-01、key-02 不受影响，只有 key-03 的寻址被重定位到新节点 D。一般而言，在一致哈希算法中，如果增加一个节点，受影响的数据仅仅是，会寻址到新节点和前一节点之间的数据，其它数据也不会受到影响。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ube890a0a\&quot;" id="\&quot;ube890a0a\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6a7101ab\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6a7101ab\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ub0b24ed4\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub0b24ed4\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u06570470\&quot;" id="\&quot;u06570470\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">对于 1000 万 key 的 3 节点 KV 存储，如果我们增加 1 个节点，变为 4 节点集群，只需要迁移 24.3% 的数据：</span></p>
  <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;codeblock\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22go%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%24%20go%20run%20.%2Fconsistent-hash.go%20%20-keys%2010000000%20-nodes%203%20-new-nodes%204%5Cn24.301550%25%20%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22default%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22JD5nb%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u6316bff0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6316bff0\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u336beb86\&quot;" id="\&quot;u336beb86\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u3d1ec900\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3d1ec900\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf4455594\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf4455594\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">综上可知，使用了一致哈希算法后，扩容或缩容的时候，都只需要重定位环空间中的一小部分数据。</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uca924d1b\&quot;" id="\&quot;uca924d1b\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0)\"="">也就是说，一致哈希算法具有较好的容错性和可扩展性。</span></strong></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u1748f2e6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1748f2e6\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua640a4dd\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua640a4dd\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;bihCl\&quot;" id="\&quot;bihCl\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud4883231\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud4883231\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0)\"="">虚拟节点</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u44a2b418\&quot;" id="\&quot;u44a2b418\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u61a6e92b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u61a6e92b\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">在一致哈希中，如果节点太少，容易因为节点分布不均匀造成数据访问的冷热不均，也就是说大多数访问请求都会集中少量几个节点上：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;udbb52f10\&quot;" id="\&quot;udbb52f10\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733653386842-5f521728-f11f-410b-9ff9-5448f5194b3d.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u22389674-5df7-4d17-bde2-d04dc97a02c%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u557dc0ce-6321-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A428%2C%22height%22%3A473%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A202717%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A566%2C%22originHeight%22%3A625%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A450%2C%22y%22%3A255%2C%22width%22%3A89%2C%22height%22%3A35%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A222%2C%22y%22%3A547%2C%22width%22%3A84%2C%22height%22%3A36%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A416%2C%22y%22%3A463%2C%22width%22%3A85%2C%22height%22%3A36%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22232-1%22%2C%22x%22%3A142%2C%22y%22%3A8%2C%22width%22%3A96%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f9fbfa%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uceb17a05%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u036ceedf\&quot;" id="\&quot;u036ceedf\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3943dfba\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3943dfba\&quot;">上图中可以看到，</span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub5fc4e38\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub5fc4e38\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">虽然有 3 个节点，但访问请求主要集中的节点 A 上。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u05df677f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u05df677f\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u912ef340\&quot;" id="\&quot;u912ef340\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua7de3a48\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua7de3a48\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucf3988a5\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucf3988a5\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(36,="" 41,="" 46)\"="">为了改善数据冷热不均的问题，一致性哈希常采用</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub8cbc522\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub8cbc522\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(36,="" 41,="" 46)\"="">“虚拟节点（virtual nodes）”技术</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ueac5ac44\&quot;" id="\&quot;ueac5ac44\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(36,="" 41,="" 46)\"="">。每个物理节点会在哈希环上对应多个虚拟节点，从而更加均匀地分布其负载。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u96c50ed5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u96c50ed5\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua1cc8842\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua1cc8842\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">其实，就是对每一个服务器节点计算多个哈希值，在每个计算结果位置上，都放置一个虚拟节点，并将虚拟节点映射到实际节点。比如，可以在主机名的后面增加编号，分别计算 “Node-A-01”“Node-A-02”“Node-B-01”“Node-B-02”“Node-C-01”“Node-C-02”的哈希值，于是形成 6 个虚拟节点：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u32408af7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u32408af7\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733653945898-53032574-842e-4e5a-816d-24eefc4ed381.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u789c4736-184e-4e75-bc6f-bb92d30061d%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u557dc0ce-6321-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A447.5%2C%22height%22%3A448%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A238400%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A655%2C%22originHeight%22%3A656%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%222%E4%B8%AA32-1%22%2C%22x%22%3A198%2C%22y%22%3A16%2C%22width%22%3A127%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22NODE-%22%2C%22x%22%3A57%2C%22y%22%3A465%2C%22width%22%3A78%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22B-02%22%2C%22x%22%3A309%2C%22y%22%3A598%2C%22width%22%3A71%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22NODE%22%2C%22x%22%3A33%2C%22y%22%3A251%2C%22width%22%3A73%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22C-02%22%2C%22x%22%3A33%2C%22y%22%3A290%2C%22width%22%3A72%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22NODE%22%2C%22x%22%3A306%2C%22y%22%3A558%2C%22width%22%3A74%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22NODE%22%2C%22x%22%3A492%2C%22y%22%3A468%2C%22width%22%3A74%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22NODE%22%2C%22x%22%3A408%2C%22y%22%3A83%2C%22width%22%3A75%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22A-02%22%2C%22x%22%3A540%2C%22y%22%3A292%2C%22width%22%3A75%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22A-01%22%2C%22x%22%3A411%2C%22y%22%3A123%2C%22width%22%3A75%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22B-07%22%2C%22x%22%3A494%2C%22y%22%3A507%2C%22width%22%3A72%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22NODE%E4%B8%80%22%2C%22x%22%3A538%2C%22y%22%3A253%2C%22width%22%3A77%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22C-01%22%2C%22x%22%3A61%2C%22y%22%3A506%2C%22width%22%3A70%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fbfdfd%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u00f1d063%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u9aa63bb5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9aa63bb5\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u969526a4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u969526a4\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">这时，如果有访问请求寻址到“Node-A-01”或者“Node-A-02”这两个虚拟节点，都将被</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1d4becbb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1d4becbb\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">重定位</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u095a770d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u095a770d\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">到节点 A。增加了节点后，节点在哈希环上的分布就</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1537df7d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1537df7d\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">相对均匀</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub5f803f1\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub5f803f1\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">了。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u4b1b0c55\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4b1b0c55\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4c1de41f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4c1de41f\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u1d885c87\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1d885c87\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u64f2a04e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u64f2a04e\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">综上可知，当节点数越多的时候，使用哈希算法时，需要迁移的数据就越多，使用一致哈希时，需要迁移的数据就越少：</span></p>
  <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;codeblock\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22go%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%24%20go%20run%20.%2Fhash.go%20%20-keys%2010000000%20-nodes%203%20-new-nodes%204%5Cn74.999980%25%5Cn%24%20go%20run%20.%2Fhash.go%20%20-keys%2010000000%20-nodes%2010%20-new-nodes%2011%5Cn90.909000%25%5Cn%24%20go%20run%20.%2Fconsistent-hash.go%20%20-keys%2010000000%20-nodes%203%20-new-nodes%204%5Cn24.301550%25%5Cn%24%20go%20run%20.%2Fconsistent-hash.go%20%20-keys%2010000000%20-nodes%2010%20-new-nodes%2011%5Cn6.479330%25%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22default%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22mnPAv%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua03c6dd8\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua03c6dd8\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4f89cb3c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4f89cb3c\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">当向 10 个节点集群中增加节点时，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub048ddc4\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub048ddc4\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0)\"="">如果使用了哈希算法，需要迁移高达 90.91% 的数据，使用一致哈希的话，只需要迁移 6.48% 的数据。</span></strong></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ubac7cf2c\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubac7cf2c\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub23554d4\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub23554d4\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(0,="" 0,="" 0)\"="">​</span></strong><br /></p>
  <blockquote data-lake-id="\&quot;u7e4e003e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7e4e003e\&quot;">
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ude4b5b6f\&quot;" id="\&quot;ude4b5b6f\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue5a00349\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue5a00349\&quot;">参考文章：</span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;bookmarkInline\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22mode%22%3A%22title%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2F100046101%2F207426%2F%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2F100046101%2F207426%2F%22%2C%22detail%22%3A%7B%22icon%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2Ffavicon.ico%22%2C%22image%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic001.geekbang.org%2Fresource%2Fimage%2F17%2Ff1%2F177e0cbd325e814005bf81c0da9f60f1.jpg%22%2C%22title%22%3A%2210%20%7C%20%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E5%93%88%E5%B8%8C%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9A%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%88%86%E7%BE%A4%EF%BC%8C%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E9%A2%86%E5%AF%BC%E8%80%85%E2%80%9D%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%9F%22%2C%22belong%22%3A%22%E6%9E%81%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%B7%B2%E5%AE%8C%E7%BB%93%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E9%99%90%E6%97%B6%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB%22%2C%22belong_url%22%3Anull%2C%22desc%22%3A%22%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E5%93%88%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%AC%E8%B4%A8%E4%B8%8A%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%AF%BB%E5%9D%80%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%82%E5%90%88%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E7%9A%84%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%AF%BB%E5%9D%80%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF%EF%BC%8C%E6%AF%94%E5%A6%82%E5%9C%A8KV%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%83%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E6%98%AF%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E3%80%82%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2F100046101%2F207426%2F%22%2C%22extra%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22_serializer%22%3A%22web.editor_link_detail%22%7D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22wJGFN%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  </blockquote>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uf68f3d46\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf68f3d46\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u91aaa019\&quot;" id="\&quot;u91aaa019\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <h3 data-lake-id="\&quot;KTTsC\&quot;" id="\&quot;KTTsC\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua67b3226\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua67b3226\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">Gossip</span></h3>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;LwkkY\&quot;" id="\&quot;LwkkY\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u23f43168\&quot;" id="\&quot;u23f43168\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">诞生背景</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u31b02048\&quot;" id="\&quot;u31b02048\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;udf76ce05\&quot;" id="\&quot;udf76ce05\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">为了实现 BASE 理论中的“最终一致性原则”。两阶段提交协议和 Raft 算法需要满足“大多数服务节点正常运行”原则，如果希望系统在少数服务节点正常运行的情况下，仍能对外提供稳定服务，这时就需要实现</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5bb8e80a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5bb8e80a\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">最终一致性</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u693c089e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u693c089e\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">。 </span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u49fce8a0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u49fce8a0\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0aeabfd6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0aeabfd6\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">Gossip 协议，顾名思义，就像流言蜚语一样，利用一种</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u36eacfe5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u36eacfe5\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">随机、带有传染性</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u94aa56e5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u94aa56e5\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">的方式，将信息传播到整个网络中，并在一定时间内，使得系统内的所有节点数据一致。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u01de5f86\&quot;" id="\&quot;u01de5f86\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;EwDlS\&quot;" id="\&quot;EwDlS\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u55d25cae\&quot;" id="\&quot;u55d25cae\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">一致实现</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u594d8acb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u594d8acb\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u29499a6a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u29499a6a\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">Gossip 实现最终一致性的三板斧分别是：直接邮寄（Direct Mail）、反熵（Anti-entropy）和谣言传播（Rumor mongering）。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua867f4ea\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua867f4ea\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u57772d25\&quot;" id="\&quot;u57772d25\&quot;">详细说明：</span></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;uf22bbd85\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u6f96fcb6\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ue6726be4\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue6726be4\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3a3de080\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3a3de080\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">直接邮寄</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf990ed68\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf990ed68\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(36,="" 41,="" 46)\"="">（Direct Mail）</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u81ebec29\&quot;" id="\&quot;u81ebec29\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">：即写时修复，直接发送更新数据，当数据发送失败时，将数据缓存在失败重试队列，然后重传。</span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2f9977c1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2f9977c1\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">如下图所示，节点 A 直接将更新数据发送给了节点 B、D。</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua40220e4\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua40220e4\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-indent:" 2em\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733661121804-5d43b0f9-dba3-4bfe-a287-5177d0cf8ddd.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u32b6d28a-dfb5-4a16-99df-1d1f334f7cc%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u557dc0ce-6321-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A438%2C%22height%22%3A317%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A119348%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A582%2C%22originHeight%22%3A421%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A35%2C%22y%22%3A178%2C%22width%22%3A63%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A334%2C%22y%22%3A37%2C%22width%22%3A59%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B96%22%2C%22x%22%3A317%2C%22y%22%3A353%2C%22width%22%3A59%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A452%2C%22y%22%3A133%2C%22width%22%3A59%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9D%22%2C%22x%22%3A465%2C%22y%22%3A286%2C%22width%22%3A59%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fcfcfc%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u49b02253%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;ub31cf048\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u152e015b\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u27b36a2b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u27b36a2b\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5e6c36e3\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5e6c36e3\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">注意：直接邮寄虽然实现起来比较容易，数据同步及时，</span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u645af062\&quot;" id="\&quot;u645af062\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">不需要校验数据一致性对比，性能消耗低。</span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3dad0b9d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3dad0b9d\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">但</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u174286ae\&quot;" id="\&quot;u174286ae\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">可能会因为缓存队列满了而丢数据</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucbd20317\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucbd20317\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">。也就是说，只采用直接邮寄是</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u57e6c1d6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u57e6c1d6\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">无法实现最终一致性</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc0225a38\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc0225a38\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">的。</span></li>
  </ul>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u47564c79\&quot;" id="\&quot;u47564c79\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;uf22bbd85\&quot;" start="\&quot;2\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u6f96fcb6\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;uec40549d\&quot;" id="\&quot;uec40549d\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc9bef173\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc9bef173\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">反熵机制</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u50d750b4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u50d750b4\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(36,="" 41,="" 46)\"="">（Anti-Entropy）</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u63c1ac59\&quot;" id="\&quot;u63c1ac59\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1a403343\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1a403343\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">即异步修复，集群中的节点，每隔段时间就随机选择某个其他节点，然后通过互相交换自己的所有数据来消除两者之间的差异，实现数据的最终一致性。</span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0ceccd28\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0ceccd28\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">反熵中的熵是指混乱程度，反熵就是指</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;udb6ba631\&quot;" id="\&quot;udb6ba631\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">消除不同节点中数据的差异</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua3eaa1c3\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua3eaa1c3\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">，提升节点间数据的相似度，降低熵值。</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u4b69736f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4b69736f\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-indent:" 2em\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733661273951-0ca270b5-a92c-4782-8ae7-eff9bd543bf8.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ud4da69f6-3a7e-4eaf-a8b7-6bf25250337%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u557dc0ce-6321-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A623%2C%22height%22%3A249%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A139626%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A668%2C%22originHeight%22%3A267%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9D%22%2C%22x%22%3A339%2C%22y%22%3A158%2C%22width%22%3A40%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9E%22%2C%22x%22%3A264%2C%22y%22%3A212%2C%22width%22%3A38%2C%22height%22%3A14%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A347%2C%22y%22%3A89%2C%22width%22%3A38%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221000%22%2C%22x%22%3A79%2C%22y%22%3A112%2C%22width%22%3A37%2C%22height%22%3A12%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221000%22%2C%22x%22%3A468%2C%22y%22%3A148%2C%22width%22%3A35%2C%22height%22%3A14%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ALICE%22%2C%22x%22%3A556%2C%22y%22%3A183%2C%22width%22%3A32%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22VALUE%22%2C%22x%22%3A606%2C%22y%22%3A87%2C%22width%22%3A35%2C%22height%22%3A12%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A280%2C%22y%22%3A45%2C%22width%22%3A38%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22VALUE%22%2C%22x%22%3A78%2C%22y%22%3A87%2C%22width%22%3A37%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A154%2C%22y%22%3A122%2C%22width%22%3A44%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%223000%22%2C%22x%22%3A604%2C%22y%22%3A183%2C%22width%22%3A37%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22VALUE%22%2C%22x%22%3A467%2C%22y%22%3A124%2C%22width%22%3A37%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22KEU%22%2C%22x%22%3A558%2C%22y%22%3A87%2C%22width%22%3A29%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22BOB%22%2C%22x%22%3A421%2C%22y%22%3A149%2C%22width%22%3A27%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22BOB%22%2C%22x%22%3A558%2C%22y%22%3A112%2C%22width%22%3A28%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%222000%22%2C%22x%22%3A605%2C%22y%22%3A206%2C%22width%22%3A39%2C%22height%22%3A12%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22JERRY%22%2C%22x%22%3A554%2C%22y%22%3A206%2C%22width%22%3A35%2C%22height%22%3A11%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22JERRY%22%2C%22x%22%3A26%2C%22y%22%3A159%2C%22width%22%3A38%2C%22height%22%3A15%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%223000%22%2C%22x%22%3A78%2C%22y%22%3A135%2C%22width%22%3A37%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22BOB%22%2C%22x%22%3A30%2C%22y%22%3A111%2C%22width%22%3A27%2C%22height%22%3A14%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%229000%22%2C%22x%22%3A603%2C%22y%22%3A160%2C%22width%22%3A41%2C%22height%22%3A12%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%225000%22%2C%22x%22%3A606%2C%22y%22%3A136%2C%22width%22%3A37%2C%22height%22%3A12%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%229000%22%2C%22x%22%3A469%2C%22y%22%3A198%2C%22width%22%3A35%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22KEU%22%2C%22x%22%3A31%2C%22y%22%3A87%2C%22width%22%3A27%2C%22height%22%3A14%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%222000%22%2C%22x%22%3A77%2C%22y%22%3A161%2C%22width%22%3A38%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%225000%22%2C%22x%22%3A470%2C%22y%22%3A173%2C%22width%22%3A35%2C%22height%22%3A12%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221000%22%2C%22x%22%3A607%2C%22y%22%3A111%2C%22width%22%3A38%2C%22height%22%3A12%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22LUCY%22%2C%22x%22%3A557%2C%22y%22%3A160%2C%22width%22%3A31%2C%22height%22%3A12%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22CKCY%22%2C%22x%22%3A420%2C%22y%22%3A199%2C%22width%22%3A30%2C%22height%22%3A10%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ALICE%22%2C%22x%22%3A29%2C%22y%22%3A136%2C%22width%22%3A34%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22OM%22%2C%22x%22%3A558%2C%22y%22%3A137%2C%22width%22%3A30%2C%22height%22%3A11%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221O%22%2C%22x%22%3A420%2C%22y%22%3A175%2C%22width%22%3A30%2C%22height%22%3A11%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22KEU%22%2C%22x%22%3A420%2C%22y%22%3A125%2C%22width%22%3A30%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fdfdfc%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u1b7fbbbb%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;u7328cd00\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;ub54f54ff\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u94f2225c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u94f2225c\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf84fcc8f\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf84fcc8f\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">实现反熵的时候，主要有推、拉、推拉三种实现方式。</span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufedc94ee\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufedc94ee\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">以修复下图中 2 个数据副本的不一致为例说明：</span></li>
  </ul>
