  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uc4d28e3d\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc4d28e3d\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc11b0ccc\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc11b0ccc\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;ud27b242c\&quot;" start="\&quot;3\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u3535b30e\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;uf8b83a71\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf8b83a71\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uee97aa23\&quot;" id="\&quot;uee97aa23\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">谣言传播</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u88c5f711\&quot;" id="\&quot;u88c5f711\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(36,="" 41,="" 46)\"="">（Epidemic Gossip）</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub3904637\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub3904637\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u24566add\&quot;" id="\&quot;u24566add\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">指的是当一个节点有了新数据后，这个节点变成</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u37f6c5b3\&quot;" id="\&quot;u37f6c5b3\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">活跃状态</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3ff91285\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3ff91285\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">，并</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ubddf0c09\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubddf0c09\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">周期性</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9f2f3d15\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9f2f3d15\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(76,="" 76,="" 76)\"="">地联系其他节点向其发送新数据，直到所有的节点都存储了该新数据。由于谣言传播非常具有传染性，它适合动态变化的分布式系统。如下图，</span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u02a6331f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u02a6331f\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">节点 A 向节点 B、D 发送新数据，节点 B 收到新数据后，变成活跃节点，然后节点 B 向节点 C、D 发送新数据。</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u4b256892\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4b256892\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-indent:" 2em\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733662223666-7b0133fc-6390-4d26-86df-e324d05b8512.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ub76ad885-c25c-43cb-b97c-edec6a4d471%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u557dc0ce-6321-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A434%2C%22height%22%3A319%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A130287%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A590%2C%22originHeight%22%3A434%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A353%2C%22y%22%3A42%2C%22width%22%3A59%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A52%2C%22y%22%3A184%2C%22width%22%3A63%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9E%22%2C%22x%22%3A336%2C%22y%22%3A361%2C%22width%22%3A59%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A472%2C%22y%22%3A139%2C%22width%22%3A60%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9D%22%2C%22x%22%3A484%2C%22y%22%3A293%2C%22width%22%3A61%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fcfcfc%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u65996fe4%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u19408690\&quot;" id="\&quot;u19408690\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ubd9964ce\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubd9964ce\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <blockquote data-lake-id="\&quot;u9d09d51a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9d09d51a\&quot;">
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u5126fc1d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5126fc1d\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1014df8c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1014df8c\&quot;">参考文章：</span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;bookmarkInline\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22mode%22%3A%22title%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2F100046101%2F208182%2F%22%2C%22text%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2F100046101%2F208182%2F%22%2C%22detail%22%3A%7B%22icon%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2Ffavicon.ico%22%2C%22image%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic001.geekbang.org%2Fresource%2Fimage%2Fdf%2F76%2Fdfe50aaf008ecb1094eb817b301e4c76.jpg%22%2C%22title%22%3A%2211%20%7C%20Gossip%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE%EF%BC%9A%E6%B5%81%E8%A8%80%E8%9C%9A%E8%AF%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%8E%9F%E6%9D%A5%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E6%80%A7%22%2C%22belong%22%3A%22%E6%9E%81%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%B7%B2%E5%AE%8C%E7%BB%93%E8%AF%BE%E7%A8%8B%E9%99%90%E6%97%B6%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB%22%2C%22belong_url%22%3Anull%2C%22desc%22%3A%22%E5%BD%93%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E6%98%AF%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%96%E8%80%85%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E6%95%B0%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E5%A4%9A%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E6%97%B6%E8%A6%81%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E8%B0%A3%E8%A8%80%E4%BC%A0%E6%92%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8C%E6%AD%A5%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E6%9C%80%E7%BB%88%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E3%80%82%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ffreegeektime.com%2F100046101%2F208182%2F%22%2C%22extra%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22_serializer%22%3A%22web.editor_link_detail%22%7D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Cb4Uv%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  </blockquote>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u8b195f18\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8b195f18\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ubfb4d71b\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubfb4d71b\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <h3 data-lake-id="\&quot;rQZRH\&quot;" id="\&quot;rQZRH\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud6b2c3c1\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud6b2c3c1\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">Quorum NWR</span></h3>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;vnrPR\&quot;" id="\&quot;vnrPR\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uafde45c2\&quot;" id="\&quot;uafde45c2\&quot;">基本介绍</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u41095e0f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u41095e0f\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u228d5d11\&quot;" id="\&quot;u228d5d11\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(36,="" 41,="" 46)\"="">Quorum NWR 模型是一种在系统中用于管理数据一致性和可用性的方法。它帮助系统在数据复制、多节点环境下，确定如何确保数据的一致性以及如何处理读写请求。当 AP 型分布式系统需要保证数据强一致性的时候，可以通过 </span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9a518de2\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9a518de2\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">Quorum NWR 自定义一致性级别。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ub3862190\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub3862190\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8d36bdd6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8d36bdd6\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;nCuQS\&quot;" id="\&quot;nCuQS\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u22232267\&quot;" id="\&quot;u22232267\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">三大要素</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ude7be473\&quot;" id="\&quot;ude7be473\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;udf0eb4b9\&quot;" id="\&quot;udf0eb4b9\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">Quorum NWR 中的三个要素，N、W、R。</span></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;u2ea13313\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u6a9f5411\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ue754c7d3\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue754c7d3\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u256d8771\&quot;" id="\&quot;u256d8771\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">N，</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud5636dd0\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud5636dd0\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">表示副本数，又叫做</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u096bd231\&quot;" id="\&quot;u096bd231\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">复制因子（Replication Factor）</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u818694e2\&quot;" id="\&quot;u818694e2\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">。</span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u28b40515\&quot;" id="\&quot;u28b40515\&quot;" class="\&quot;lake-fontsize-11\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(5,="" 7,="" 59)\"="">指定数据要被复制的节点数。即</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3d670921\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3d670921\&quot;" class="\&quot;lake-fontsize-11\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(5,="" 7,="" 59)\"="">每份数据在系统中将存储多少个副本</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u787f476f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u787f476f\&quot;" class="\&quot;lake-fontsize-11\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(5,="" 7,="" 59)\"="">。如下图，</span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0c100e5d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0c100e5d\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">在这个三节点的集群中，DATA-1 有 2 个副本，DATA-2 有 3 个副本，DATA-3 有 1 个副本。也就是说，副本数可以不等于节点数，不同的数据可以有不同的副本数（指定数据的副本数可</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u62b65126\&quot;" id="\&quot;u62b65126\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">自定义</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2a18ca82\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2a18ca82\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">）。</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u12b446ba\&quot;" id="\&quot;u12b446ba\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-indent:" 2em\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733818720785-4ca62fe5-0628-4ba2-8cab-23ed07fe6c02.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u93b73281-f86a-408b-95c7-1391c48c1ff%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u9f29d3e4-bf56-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A476.5%2C%22height%22%3A289%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A139993%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A581%2C%22originHeight%22%3A352%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A138%2C%22y%22%3A197%2C%22width%22%3A48%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A445%2C%22y%22%3A196%2C%22width%22%3A49%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA-3%22%2C%22x%22%3A289%2C%22y%22%3A112%2C%22width%22%3A54%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA-2%22%2C%22x%22%3A442%2C%22y%22%3A271%2C%22width%22%3A53%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA-2%22%2C%22x%22%3A134%2C%22y%22%3A274%2C%22width%22%3A52%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A291%2C%22y%22%3A29%2C%22width%22%3A50%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA-2%22%2C%22x%22%3A288%2C%22y%22%3A76%2C%22width%22%3A52%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA-1%22%2C%22x%22%3A442%2C%22y%22%3A232%2C%22width%22%3A52%2C%22height%22%3A14%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA-1%22%2C%22x%22%3A134%2C%22y%22%3A237%2C%22width%22%3A52%2C%22height%22%3A12%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fcf8f6%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u0ed264c9%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;u2ea13313\&quot;" start="\&quot;2\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u6a9f5411\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;uee5a1260\&quot;" id="\&quot;uee5a1260\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5e4238ab\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5e4238ab\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">W</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue025a0bc\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue025a0bc\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">，又称</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc566e947\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc566e947\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">写一致性级别（Write Consistency Level）</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub660e21d\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub660e21d\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">，表示成功</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5edaebc6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5edaebc6\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">完成 W 个副本更新</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u81d7e394\&quot;" id="\&quot;u81d7e394\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">，才完成写操作。如下图，DATA-2 的写副本数 W 为 2，对 DATA-2 执行写操作时，完成了 2 个副本的更新（比如节点 A、C），才完成写操作。</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u8019b589\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8019b589\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-indent:" 2em\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733819065855-e0b187f6-f725-4286-8b06-dc4d5ca43f6f.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u15e5fac7-c204-443c-aec7-2798c384a5e%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u9f29d3e4-bf56-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A475.5%2C%22height%22%3A298%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A138005%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A539%2C%22originHeight%22%3A338%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A423%2C%22y%22%3A190%2C%22width%22%3A49%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22URITELEVEL%3DZ%22%2C%22x%22%3A130%2C%22y%22%3A70%2C%22width%22%3A89%2C%22height%22%3A11%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A275%2C%22y%22%3A27%2C%22width%22%3A48%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA-2%22%2C%22x%22%3A272%2C%22y%22%3A72%2C%22width%22%3A52%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA-2%22%2C%22x%22%3A123%2C%22y%22%3A265%2C%22width%22%3A53%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA-1%22%2C%22x%22%3A122%2C%22y%22%3A228%2C%22width%22%3A53%2C%22height%22%3A12%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A126%2C%22y%22%3A190%2C%22width%22%3A48%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA-1%22%2C%22x%22%3A421%2C%22y%22%3A225%2C%22width%22%3A51%2C%22height%22%3A12%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA-3%22%2C%22x%22%3A273%2C%22y%22%3A109%2C%22width%22%3A51%2C%22height%22%3A12%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA-2%22%2C%22x%22%3A422%2C%22y%22%3A262%2C%22width%22%3A51%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fcf7f5%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ubd28b147%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;u2ea13313\&quot;" start="\&quot;3\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u6a9f5411\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ua78dd26d\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua78dd26d\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0c19854d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0c19854d\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">R，</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8d21e1db\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8d21e1db\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">又称</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6d402eaf\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6d402eaf\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">读一致性级别（Read Consistency Level）</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7a6a2c12\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7a6a2c12\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">，表示读</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufb87474f\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufb87474f\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">取一个数据对象时需要读 R 个副本</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf2fa5125\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf2fa5125\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">。即读取指定数据时，要读 R 副本，然后返回 R 个副本中最新的那份数据。如下图，DATA-2 的读副本数 R 为 2。客户端读取 DATA-2 的数据时，需要读取 2 个副本中的数据，然后返回最新的那份数据。</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uebd0b95f\&quot;" id="\&quot;uebd0b95f\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-indent:" 2em\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1733819281792-6b535b81-fa8d-46bb-abc7-2df903f00393.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ue821ec68-6fb3-4227-b44d-fcb9380254e%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u9f29d3e4-bf56-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A483%2C%22height%22%3A291%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A152898%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A574%2C%22originHeight%22%3A346%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22READLEVEL2%22%2C%22x%22%3A154%2C%22y%22%3A90%2C%22width%22%3A74%2C%22height%22%3A51%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9A%22%2C%22x%22%3A301%2C%22y%22%3A22%2C%22width%22%3A50%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA-2%22%2C%22x%22%3A142%2C%22y%22%3A271%2C%22width%22%3A55%2C%22height%22%3A14%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA-2%22%2C%22x%22%3A455%2C%22y%22%3A268%2C%22width%22%3A52%2C%22height%22%3A14%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA-1%22%2C%22x%22%3A455%2C%22y%22%3A229%2C%22width%22%3A53%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA-2%22%2C%22x%22%3A298%2C%22y%22%3A70%2C%22width%22%3A54%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA-1%22%2C%22x%22%3A142%2C%22y%22%3A232%2C%22width%22%3A52%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A458%2C%22y%22%3A193%2C%22width%22%3A49%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9C%22%2C%22x%22%3A145%2C%22y%22%3A193%2C%22width%22%3A51%2C%22height%22%3A20%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DATA-3%22%2C%22x%22%3A300%2C%22y%22%3A107%2C%22width%22%3A53%2C%22height%22%3A13%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fbf6f4%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u4e472880%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua3911e5e\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua3911e5e\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"=""><br /><br /></span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua2e0efa0\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua2e0efa0\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufa09cb66\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufa09cb66\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">综上可知，无论客户端如何执行读操作，哪怕它访问的是写操作</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u70d3145f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u70d3145f\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">未强制更新</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc277dd54\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc277dd54\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">副本数据的节点（比如节点 B），但因为 W(2) + R(2) &gt; N(3)，当访问节点 B，执行读操作时，因为要读 2 份数据副本，所以除了节点 B 上的 DATA-2，还会读取节点 A 或节点 C 上的 DATA-2，就像上图的样子（比如节点 C 上的 DATA-2），而节点 A 和节点 C 的 DATA-2 数据副本是</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc1c8e668\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc1c8e668\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">强制更新</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7be14b9c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7be14b9c\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">成功的。此时返回给客户端肯定是最新的那份数据。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u8b84e832\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8b84e832\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue4e184b0\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue4e184b0\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u35a60daa\&quot;" id="\&quot;u35a60daa\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u20fc7938\&quot;" id="\&quot;u20fc7938\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">N、W、R 值的不同组合，会产生不同的一致性效果，具体来说，有这么两种效果：</span></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;u9103c804\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;ufc96345e\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u32c73437\&quot;" id="\&quot;u32c73437\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uadb299af\&quot;" id="\&quot;uadb299af\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">当 W + R &gt; N 的时候，对于客户端来讲，整个系统能保证强一致性，一定能返回更新后的那份数据。</span></li>
   <li fid="\&quot;ufc96345e\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ubddcb196\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubddcb196\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u44c3085d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u44c3085d\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">当 W + R &lt;= N 的时候，对于客户端来讲，整个系统只能保证最终一致性，可能会返回旧数据。</span></li>
  </ul>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u0cf4e7b5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0cf4e7b5\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4810964f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4810964f\&quot;" style="\&quot;color:" rgb(53,="" 53,="" 53)\"="">​</span><br /></p>
  <h3 data-lake-id="\&quot;RwoJ8\&quot;" id="\&quot;RwoJ8\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua93234ef\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua93234ef\&quot;">ZAB（未完）</span></h3>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;t4fbn\&quot;" id="\&quot;t4fbn\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7619a178\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7619a178\&quot;">基本介绍</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u2167913a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2167913a\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5af53629\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5af53629\&quot;">Zab 协议 的全称是 Zookeeper Atomic Broadcast （Zookeeper 原子广播协议）。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ub7041590\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub7041590\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ubb891f51\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubb891f51\&quot;">Zab 协议是专门为分布式协调服务Zookeeper设计的一种支持崩溃恢复的原子广播协议 ，其主要作用是保证Zookeeper 集群及崩溃恢复的数据一致性。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u42f84f0d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u42f84f0d\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud987c02d\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud987c02d\&quot;">基于该协议，Zookeeper 实现了一种</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uddc2a518\&quot;" id="\&quot;uddc2a518\&quot;">主从模式</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u82b3edf9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u82b3edf9\&quot;">的系统架构（即 Leader 和 Follower 模型），确保集群内各个副本的数据一致性。该架构中的主从模式指的是，只有 Leader 节点负责处理外部的写事务请求，随后 Leader 将数据同步给其他 Follower 节点。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ub68b4d5b\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub68b4d5b\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u11aeb080\&quot;" id="\&quot;u11aeb080\&quot;">Zookeeper 客户端会随机连接到集群中的某个节点，如果请求是读取操作，则直接从当前节点获取数据；如果是写入操作，该节点会将事务提交给 Leader。Leader 接收到事务后进行广播，只要超过半数的节点成功写入，该事务便会被确认提交。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u22c0a676\&quot;" id="\&quot;u22c0a676\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1734780307181-b2b6ed88-6402-4e89-8944-0f8a6603ffbe.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u08562d5c-c10c-4b77-8b67-b9640f13689%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u176424f7-5f4c-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A544%2C%22height%22%3A310%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A120030%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A680%2C%22originHeight%22%3A387%2C%22ratio%22%3A1%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22%E5%86%99%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%20%E5%86%99%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%20%E5%86%99%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%20LEADER%20%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6%20%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6%20%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6%20%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6%20FOLLOWER%20FOLLOWER%20FOLLOWER%20FOLLOWER%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A413%2C%22y%22%3A128%2C%22width%22%3A37%2C%22height%22%3A15%2C%22text%22%3A%22%E5%86%99%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A307%2C%22y%22%3A130%2C%22width%22%3A40%2C%22height%22%3A16%2C%22text%22%3A%22%E5%86%99%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A199%2C%22y%22%3A130%2C%22width%22%3A39%2C%22height%22%3A16%2C%22text%22%3A%22%E5%86%99%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A304%2C%22y%22%3A193%2C%22width%22%3A46%2C%22height%22%3A14%2C%22text%22%3A%22LEADER%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A449%2C%22y%22%3A265%2C%22width%22%3A26%2C%22height%22%3A15%2C%22text%22%3A%22%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A371%2C%22y%22%3A266%2C%22width%22%3A27%2C%22height%22%3A17%2C%22text%22%3A%22%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A192%2C%22y%22%3A269%2C%22width%22%3A27%2C%22height%22%3A16%2C%22text%22%3A%22%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A286%2C%22y%22%3A271%2C%22width%22%3A27%2C%22height%22%3A15%2C%22text%22%3A%22%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A577%2C%22y%22%3A343%2C%22width%22%3A55%2C%22height%22%3A19%2C%22text%22%3A%22FOLLOWER%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A414%2C%22y%22%3A347%2C%22width%22%3A53%2C%22height%22%3A14%2C%22text%22%3A%22FOLLOWER%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A60%2C%22y%22%3A349%2C%22width%22%3A51%2C%22height%22%3A14%2C%22text%22%3A%22FOLLOWER%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A239%2C%22y%22%3A350%2C%22width%22%3A53%2C%22height%22%3A15%2C%22text%22%3A%22FOLLOWER%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fbfbf9%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u51bea45c%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u2eed4491\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2eed4491\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;JdqMn\&quot;" id="\&quot;JdqMn\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0f0cbaf9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0f0cbaf9\&quot;">顺序保证</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua040b64a\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua040b64a\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uf70eae3d\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf70eae3d\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ue23be3c1\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue23be3c1\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;Hlyw3\&quot;" id="\&quot;Hlyw3\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u062a7adb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u062a7adb\&quot;">领导选举</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u3d07a16a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3d07a16a\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <blockquote data-lake-id="\&quot;u338b1e1a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u338b1e1a\&quot;">
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u521f19e8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u521f19e8\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucabeb196\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucabeb196\&quot;">参考文章：</span>
